rame width=\"711\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4GlXOOYL_5I\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/FsHgiIQ.jpg)\n\n##### 惡夢蝙蝠俠身穿蝙蝠裝與黃色大衣，黃色大衣與工裝褲、戰術腰帶，都與沙漠中的配色相近，大衣嵌有可彎曲的金屬絲，可自由做出具動態感的形狀，可能是考慮到機動性，蝙蝠裝大部分採用軟材質，大腿配有槍套。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1P6WqKs.jpg)\n\n##### 超人身穿黑色超人裝，兩側腹部有不明顯的淺色線條延伸到大腿，兩手臂也有環狀的淺色線條，胸前有銀色的標誌性S型圖案，頭雕完全按照演員亨利·卡維爾（Henry Cavill）的臉部細節打造，熱視線版的頭雕內有可發亮的LED，讓即將發射熱視線的超人更加逼真。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/s431SDH.jpg)\n\n##### 尺寸：蝙蝠俠高32公分 超人高31.5公分\n##### 預購價格：3,200港幣 約11,691新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2022年第三季-第四季\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/HgXRKRF.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/8WoYJKe.jpg)\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/n4pQoDG.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hhJ8VCu.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6Pxk1pk.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6BKSIET.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/S0LeCGZ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/YX30Cit.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ureJ9T4.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/CKHilOB.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/k3JSqFb.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hF6OUZl.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/dRi0ljT.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SIxVNtK.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/WaVfAOq.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/s0MaL8U.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/asonrQq.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/LB2gQnY.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/JPCOJJS.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/TS0BSBK.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/eBxNIWD.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/w1xv9Cg.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Xgr6xVW.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ColRcas.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/RzH4Tut.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1gralQm.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/kJS4PSy.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/DWWlOQd.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/fvUhukr.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6Abx6Ja