\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4TxQikW.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/no1Pyu5.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mqBSzMv.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wiDG6mE.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Medicom Toy**](http://www.medicomtoy.co.jp/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/Q1dQG2P.png','','新聞','2021-03-25 11:41:58',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',31,7),(477,'超越極限！《我的英雄學院》「綠谷出久＆爆豪勝己＆轟焦凍」豪華版1/4比例全身雕像 Prime 1 Studio新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 日本雕像品牌**Prime 1 Studio**專製時下最具話題的熱門人物雕像，昨日在[**官網**](https://www.prime1studio.com/)發布旗下**My Hero Academia（我的英雄學院）系列**開放預購的 **《我的英雄學院》「綠谷出久＆爆豪勝己＆轟焦凍」豪華版1/4比例全身雕像**官方圖片與訊息，將於2022年6月-9月發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/XXN4oFK.jpg)\n\n##### “PLUS ULTRA（超越極限）!!!”\n\n##### Prime 1 Studio自豪地介紹了我們最受歡迎的日本動漫特許經營權之一 – 我的英雄學院的第一個雕像！雕像展示了雄英高校 英雄科1年A班最有前途的三個學生：綠谷出久：笨久、爆豪勝己：大爆殺神、轟焦凍：焦凍。\n\n##### 我們錯綜複雜的雕像展示了嶄露頭角的英雄綠谷出久、爆豪勝己和轟焦凍，以及他們的個性。綠谷出久全力以赴，爆豪勝己引發爆炸，轟焦凍雙重揮舞半燃！\n\n##### 豪華版允許您更改綠谷出久、爆豪勝己、轟焦凍的強度等級。綠谷出久表現出了敏銳的專注，爆豪勝己咬緊了雙拳，轟焦凍咬緊牙關，期待一場激烈的戰鬥，而轟焦凍則表現出他的鎮定和戰術方式。此外，豪華版還將獲得一個替換頭雕，描繪出綠谷一直以來都想成為的：英雄！\n\n##### 這三個冠軍從一個以雄英高校為主題的底座中冒出，並以紀念碑為主題，以紀念他們中最偉大的英雄：歐爾麥特！\n\n##### 對於所有“我的英雄學院”粉絲來說，這個立體雕像都是不可否認的聖杯！\n\n##### 規格：\n##### 1個雄英的主題設計底座\n##### 3個額外替換頭雕（綠谷出久、爆豪勝己、轟焦凍）\n##### 1個綠谷出久替換頭雕[僅限豪華版]\n\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qn9bXeo.jpg)\n\n\n##### **【原文】**\n\n##### “PLUS ULTRA!!!\"\"\n\n##### Prime 1 Studio is proud to introduce our premiere diorama of one of the most popular Japanese anime franchises – My Hero Academia! The diorama features three of UA Class 1-A’s most promising students: Izuku Midoriya: Deku, Katsuki Bakugo: Great Explosion Murder God Dynamight and Shoto Todoroki: Shoto.\n\n##### Our intricately-detailed statue showcases budding heroes Deku, Dynamight, and Shoto, their trademark Quirks on full display! Deku charges up One for All, Dynamight ignites Explosion and Shoto double-wields Half-Cold Half-Hot!\n\n##### The Deluxe Version allows you to change up Deku, Dynamight and Shoto’s intensity levels. With their additional swappable heads, Deku exhibits his keen focus, Dynamight grits his teeth in anticipation of a fierce fight and Shoto displays his trademark calm & tactical manner. In addition, receive a Bonus switchout head portraying Deku’s characteristic exuberance at being what he has always wanted to be: a Hero!\n\n##### These three champions spring forth from a UA-themed base, anchored by a monument in honor of the greatest Hero of them all: All Might!\n\n##### This diorama is an undeniable grail item for all My Hero Academia fans!\n\n##### Specifications:\n##### One (1) designed UA themed base\n##### Three (3) additional swappable heads (Midoriya, Bakugo, Todoroki)\n##### One (1) Bonus swappable Midoriya head [Deluxe Bonus Version Only]\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BD4FdKm.jpg)\n\n##### 尺寸：高68.8公分｜寬56.9公分｜長54.6公分\n##### 預購價格：1,099美元 約31,436新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2022年6月-9月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/t5nos2x.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/0kR2eJP.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NLTcidp.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/voSrDfS.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/39CtAQ4.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/8dYCV6g.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Z2RpbEh.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/oxAZc0k.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/r6zOB78.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SLcaSQG.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/foWojwi.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/OMOtjnf.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/l06jUCt.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/eL4q3Va.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.im