79)','https://i.imgur.com/aBWeKd6.png','https://i.imgur.com/UHW9kwx.png','新聞','2021-03-25 17:33:33',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',117,7),(482,'《查克·史奈德之正義聯盟》「蝙蝠俠＆超人＆閃電俠」1/12比例可動人偶 Mezco Toyz新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 擅長製造恐怖角色的美式廠牌**Mezco Toyz**，昨日在[**官網**](https://www.mezcotoyz.com/?fbclid=IwAR1VdM1ZQafSlD2AW5V-FrRDsd0Nr2C5klK2xxZTcszALX987LzIyEWUIXU)發布旗下**One:12 Collective廠牌**開放預購的 **《查克·史奈德之正義聯盟》「蝙蝠俠＆超人＆閃電俠」1/12比例可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，將於2022年1月-3月發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/shBMGgV.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/MtU6Qdy.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Tsa3b54.jpg)\n\n##### “他從未與我們作戰。不團結我們”\n\n##### 尊敬的導演查克·史奈德（Zack Snyder）對他的電影《正義聯盟》的構想，Mezco Toyz自豪地在這套豪華鋼盒裝的收藏家作品中展示了蝙蝠俠、超人、閃電俠！\n\n##### 正如在查克·史奈德的正義聯盟中所看到的那樣，這三位英雄都是新服裝的。 \n\n##### 被復活後，超人穿著黑色的金屬色恢復服，讓他恢復體力和精力。他的衣服在斗篷中配有一體式擺線，可最大程度地發揮展示作用。 \n\n##### 蝙蝠俠裝備升級版蝙蝠裝，具有增強的防護能力和吸能的手套。像斗篷一樣的皮革也內置有金屬絲。 \n\n##### 閃電俠身穿特製套裝，可保護神速力駕駛者以超人般的速度移動而不會造成傷害。 \n\n##### 每個成員都具有多個新的頭雕，包括超人的熱視線頭雕和與班·艾佛列克（Ben Affleck）相似的無頭套的布魯斯·韋恩頭雕。\n\n##### 正義聯盟DSB套裝隨附特定於角色的配件，包括具有LED功能的母盒等。\n\n \n##### ONE：12個集體正義聯盟豪華鋼製盒裝套裝備配：\n##### 蝙蝠俠：1:12具有30多個關節的素體、3個替換頭雕、手繪正宗細節、約高17cm、替換手x7（1對擺姿勢的手、1個握住槍的手（R）、1對拳頭、1對手握著手（L＆R））\n##### 超人：1:12具有32個以上關節點的素體、3個替換頭雕、手繪正宗細節、約高17cm、3對替換手(1對拳頭、1對飛手、1對抓手）\n##### 閃電俠：1:12具有30多個關節的素體、2個頭雕、手繪正宗細節、約15cm高、替換手x7（1對拳頭、1對擺姿勢的手、1對跑步手、1個指向手（R））\n \n\n##### 服裝：\n##### 蝙蝠俠：頭套（貼在頭像上）、仿皮斗篷（帶有一體式金屬絲）、帶標誌性圖案的蝙蝠服、手腕手套、戰術腰帶、膝蓋高的靴子\n##### 超人：修身超人裝（帶有“艾爾家族”標誌性圖案）、帶有一體式擺線的斗篷、小腿中筒靴\n##### 閃光：防護服與一體式軟體、閃電圖案\n \n\n\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ffTeOg1.jpg)\n\n##### **【原文】**\n\n##### “He’s never fought us. Not us united”\n\n##### Honoring director Zack Snyder’s opus vision of his film the Justice League, Mezco Toyz proudly presents Batman, Superman, and The Flash in this Deluxe Steel Boxed collector\'s set!\n\n##### All three heroes are newly outfitted as they are seen in Zack Snyder’s Justice League. \n\n##### After being resurrected, Superman wears his Kryptonian recovery suit in black with metal tones, allowing him to regain his strength and energy. His outfit features a integrated posing wire in his cape for maximum display options. \n\n##### Batman is outfitted in an upgraded Batsuit with protection enhancements and energy absorbing gauntlets. The leather like cape has a posing wire built into it as well. \n\n##### The Flash is protected in a a specialy-made suit allowing the speedster to move at superhuman speeds without harm. \n\n##### Each member features multiple new head portraits including a heat vision head for Superman and an unmasked Bruce Wayne portrait with the likeness of Ben Affleck.\n\n##### The Justice League DSB set comes complete with character-specific accessories including a Mother Box with light-up function and much more.\n\n \n##### THE ONE:12 COLLECTIVE JUSTICE LEAGUE DELUXE STEEL BOXED SET FEATURES:\n##### Batman\n##### One:12 Collective body with over 30 points of articulation\n##### Three (3) head portraits\n##### Hand painted authentic detailing\n##### Approximately 17cm tall\n##### Seven (7) interchangeable hands including:\n##### One (1) pair of posing hands (L&R) \n##### One (1) gun holding hand (R) \n##### One (1) pair of fists (L & R) \n##### One (1) pair of Batarang holding hands (L & R)\n##### Superman\n##### One:12 Collective body with over 32 points of articulation\n##### Three (3) head portraits\n##### Hand painted authentic detailing\n##### Approximately 17cm tall\n##### Six (6) interchangeable hands including:\n##### One (1) pair of fists (L & R)\n##### One (1) pair of flying hands (L & R)\n##### One (1) pair of grabbing hands (L & R)\n##### Flash\n##### One:12 Collective body with over 30 points of articulation\n##### Two (2) head portrait\n##### Hand painted authentic detailing\n##### Approximately 15cm tall\n##### Seven (7) interchangeable hands including \n##### One (1) pair of fists (L & R)\n##### One (1) pair of posing hands (L & R)\n##### One (1) pair of running hands (L & R)\n##### One (1) pointing hand (R)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/jPVd7Ny.jpg)\n##### 尺寸：蝙蝠俠高17公分 超人高17公分 閃電俠高15公分\n##### 預購價格：260美元 約7,439新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2022年1月-3月\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ol994oo.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hLYfoR4.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wY6MUXg.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/LpgEOOz.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Mezco Toyz**](https://www.mezcotoyz.com/?fbclid=IwAR1VdM1ZQafSlD2AW5V-FrRDsd0Nr2C5klK2xxZTcszALX987LzIyEWUIXU)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/2do51O0.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/LDH5dWd.jpg','新聞','2021-03-25 17:34:08',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',71,7),(483,'《降世神通：最後的氣宗》「安」Q-Fig Quantum Mechanix新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 位於洛杉磯的創意工作室**Quantum Mechanix**，3月18日在[**官網**](https://qmxonline.com/?fbclid=IwAR0kLNfGjjEDxpQcb4QdX8QY4kJWQMC4JXbtMfxwoNUfc1WFL881qeLccFo)發布旗下**Q-Fig系列**開放預購的 **《降世神通：最後的氣宗》「安」**官方圖片與訊息，將於2021年7月發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/onYYxCM.jpg)\n\n##### 安是光與和平精神的化身，即神通王，能夠彎曲自然界中的所有四個元素-火、水、土、空氣。他的最後族人，在設法使四個基本民族保持平衡的同時，可以輕鬆控制風向。受到尼克兒童頻道鍾愛的頭像：《降世神通：最後的氣宗》的啟發，安在我們的新Aang Q-Fig Max Elite中展示了他對空氣的掌握。 \n\n##### 雖然安天生是一名和平主義者，但如果您將他推得太遠，他的彎曲技巧是無與倫比的，並且具有爆發力。《降世神通：最後的氣宗》在我們的安 Q-Fig Max Elite身上產生了一個猛烈的漩渦，強大到足以保護自己，怒氣甚至會腐蝕石頭。風繞著昂昂吹來，將樹葉和岩石高高地舉向空中。安高高地坐在懸崖邊上，穿著游牧民族的木製長袍，與他的木棍一起彎曲旋風。雖然安可能是他族人中的最後一個族人，但他肯定並不孤單-他的忠實同伴毛毛在他上方的陣風中飛翔並滑行。 \n\n##### 巨大的安 Q-Fig Max Elite從雲層底部到毛毛伸出的翅膀尖端約高9英寸。Aang周圍的漩渦由半透明材料製成，在其所有榮耀中都捕捉到了空中彎曲的威嚴。毛毛似乎騎著氣流，越過了裝飾有截氣箭頭的安的頭。沒有任何細節可以為您的Q-Fig系列帶來《降世神通：最後的氣宗》的栩栩如生。 \n\n##### 重溫神通王的刺激：QMx的《降世神通：最後的氣宗》！\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3okkvvW.jpg)\n\n##### **【原文】**\n\n##### The incarnation of the spirit of light and peace known as the Avatar, Aang is capable of bending all four elements in nature - fire, water, earth and air. The last of his people, he can control the winds with ease as he seeks to keep the four elemental nations in balance. Inspired by Nickelodeon’s beloved Avatar: The Last Airbender, behold as Aang demonstrates his mastery of air in our new Aang Q-Fig Max Elite. \n\n##### While Aang is a pacifist by nature, his bending skills are unmatched and capable of explosive power - if you push him too far. The Last Airbender conjures a furious maelstrom in our Aang Q-Fig Max Elite, powerful enough to shield himself and with a fury that can even erode stone. The winds whip around Aang, lifting leaves and rocks high into the air. Perched high on a cliffside, Aang bends the whirlwind with his wooden staff while dressed in the traditional robes of the Air Nomads. And while Aang may be the last of his kind, he is certainly not alone - his loyal companion Momo soars and glides on the gusts high above him. \n\n##### The colossal Aang Q-Fig Max Elite stands approximately 9 inches tall from the base of the clouds to the tip of Momo’s outstretched wing. The vortex surrounding Aang is crafted in translucent material, capturing the majesty of airbending in all its glory. Momo seemingly rides the current, passing over Aang’s head which has been adorned with mastery tattoos. No detail has been spared in bringing The Last Airbender to life for your Q-Fig collection. \n\n##### Relive the excitement of Avatar: The Last Airbender with QMx!\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/M6Hhf5T.jpg)\n\n##### 尺寸：高9吋\n##### 預購價格：49.95美元 約1,431新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年7月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NCPARF1.jpg)\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3IsjeFt.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Quantum Mechanix**](https://qmxonline.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/XMw1P2v.png','https://i.imgur.com/Fv3K0n5.png','新聞','2021-03-26 08:31:46',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',19,7),(484,'最和平的忍者龜《忍者龜1987》「多納太羅」1/4比例可動人偶 NECA新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### NECA(國家娛樂收藏品協會)，3月17日在[**官網**](https://necaonline.com/)發布開放預購的 **《忍者龜1987》「多納太羅」1/4比例可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，將於2021年7月發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/2s0RdGk.jpg)\n\n##### 卡哇崩嘎，伙計！NECA自豪地宣布經典1987年的《忍者神龜》卡通中的第二個1/4比例人物！\n##### Giant Size 多納太羅身高15吋，有近30個關節，並配有四個替換的頭部配件，以描繪各種表情。\n##### 這些配件可以在Giant Size系列的所有四個忍者龜中互換！收集它們並為每隻忍者龜創建更多表情！\n##### 為他準備的配件還包括棍棒、替換雙手、披薩片以及可開關的烏龜通訊器，以及更多！那是真實，傑克！\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wj7Fjem.jpg)\n\n##### **【原文】**\n\n##### Cowabunga, dudes! NECA is proud to announce the second 1/4 scale figure from the classic 1987 Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles cartoon!\n##### Giant Size Donatello stands 15 inches tall with nearly 30 points of articulation and comes with four interchangeable top and bottom face plates to portray a variety of expressions.\n##### These face plates are interchangeable across all four Turtles in the Giant Size line! Collect them all and create even more expressions for each Turtle!\n##### Rounding out his accessories are bo staff, extra hands, slices of pizza, and a Turtle Communicator that opens and closes, and more! And that’s a fact, jack!\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/S6bGpCq.jpg)\n\n##### 尺寸：高15吋\n##### 預購價格：124.99美元 約3,574新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年7月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/F6QVsjE.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mAgrn6O.jpg)\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/PP9POuI.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6A8tkxD.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Es1AnNl.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/gb8o7Ij.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/F1WupcY.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1asvDmy.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**NECA**](https://necaonline.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/iKPYBfK.jpg','','新聞','2021-03-26 08:32:30',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',8,7),(485,'墓碑後偷看《聖誕夜驚魂》「傑克·史基靈頓」7吋雕像 NECA新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### NECA(國家娛樂收藏品協會)，昨日在[**官網**](https://necaonline.com/)發布旗下**Head Knocker系列**開放預購的 **《聖誕夜驚魂》「傑克·史基靈頓」**官方圖片與訊息，將於2021年9月發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/c9GlTYZ.jpg)\n\n##### NECA的Head Knockers系列歡迎聖誕節前唯一的《聖誕夜驚魂》中的傑克·史基靈頓（Jack Skellington）！這個可怕而令人愉快的傢伙被描繪成從墓碑後面偷看，身高超過7吋，頭頂忽隱忽現。\n\n##### Head Knockers是由手工鑄造的冷鑄樹脂製成的，具有更多細節。帶有可收集的啞光飾包裝，帶有斑點光澤。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n\n##### **【原文】**\n\n##### NECA’s line of Head Knockers welcomes the one and only Jack Skellington from The Nightmare Before Christmas! This frightful and delightful fellow is depicted peeking from behind a tombstone and is over 7 inches tall with bobbling head.\n\n##### Head Knockers are made from cold-cast resin that’s hand-painted for extra detail. Comes in collectible matte finish packaging with spot gloss.\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高7吋\n##### 預購價格：未公布\n##### 發售日期：2021年9月\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**NECA**](https://necaonline.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/TBfFIrE.png','','新聞','2021-03-26 08:33:03',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',12,7),(486,'一千年前 迷信和劍統治了…《夜行神龍》「石像鬼 戈利雅」7吋可動人偶 NECA新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### NECA(國家娛樂收藏品協會)，昨日午夜十二點在[**官網**](https://necaonline.com/)發布開放預購的 **夜行神龍》「石像鬼 戈利雅」7吋可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，將於2021年7月發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/HzXxHO6.jpg)\n\n##### “一千年前，迷信和劍統治了……” \n\n##### 石像鬼的時代又來了！石像鬼可以說1990年代最好的哥特式漫畫，它跟隨著古老的石像鬼氏族搬到了通現代的蘇格蘭，當時他們的蘇格蘭城堡被搬遷了。\n\n##### 領隊戈利雅以適當的8吋可動人偶和16吋翅膀加入了Ultimate系列！該圖具有明顯的關節，包括翅膀和尾巴，並帶有許多配件：翅膀、墨西哥胡椒、書本以及可替換的頭和手。\n\n##### 有方便觀看的透明視窗包裝盒，帶有掀開式翻蓋。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/xq9mG4k.jpg)\n\n##### **【原文】**\n\n##### “One thousand years ago, superstition and the sword ruled…” \n\n##### “The time of the Gargoyles has come again! Arguably the best gothic cartoon of the 1990s, Gargoyles followed an ancient clan of gargoyles transported to modern-day Manhattan when their Scottish castle is relocated.\n\n##### “Leader Goliath joins the Ultimate line with an appropriately large 8″ action figure, with a wingspan of 16 inches! The figure features full articulation, including on wings and tail, and comes with plenty of accessories: wings, jalapeno pepper, book, and interchangeable heads and hands.\n\n##### “Comes in display-friendly window box packaging with opening flap.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/odGh8NX.jpg)\n\n##### 尺寸：高7吋\n##### 預購價格：32.99美元 約943新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年7月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/J0uZPrM.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/JhdPe5K.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/LKF0VAi.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mDbHX6g.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/WEDKHNm.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4YYqVlq.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/u3UP5U2.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4rJuATv.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/2v9oJuY.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6c0Xbs1.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**NECA**](https://necaonline.com/)\n##### 想