first time in history, in homage to the battle-heavy, blood-soaked 1974 fan favorite GODZILLA VS. MECHAGODZILLA. Perched upon a Pacific tsunami and ready to annihilate his destructive digital doppelgänger (but just as ready to provide you with radioactive refreshment), the GODZILLA \'74 Tiki Mug is a monumental masterwork of dinosaur drinkware fit for a king.\n##### NOTE: These mugs are handmade, making each one unique. Slight variations from images shown may occur.\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/h8tQp8G.png)\n##### 尺寸：高8.25吋\n##### 預購價格：65美元 約1,856新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年5月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7WvQCMo.png)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/gutcOnK.png)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/v2PVLw4.png)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SqIEZSh.png)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ReH96uu.png)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/YoRCkn4.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Mondo**](https://mondoshop.com/collections/all/products/adventure-time-statue-jake-and-finn-regular-version#featured-video)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/e3NWOuW.png','','新聞','2021-03-29 17:17:08',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',30,7),(500,'《獵鷹與酷寒戰士》「酷寒戰士 巴奇」Cosbaby系列 Hot Toys新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 世界知名的收藏級1/6比例可動人偶的香港廠牌**Hot Toys**，3月23日在[**官網**](http://www.hottoys.com.hk/?fbclid=IwAR209xNQykEV9PgpXUxNqA0hV3lVOZmWez-jsVz-NYzzrhb9TQX22Rj7dlI)發布旗下**Cosbaby系列**開放預購的 **《獵鷹與酷寒戰士》「酷寒戰士 巴奇」**官方圖片與訊息，可在各大玩具店預購，將於2021年第二季-第三季發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Y2yivnx.jpg)\n\n##### 美國隊長最好的伙伴山姆·威爾遜（Sam Wilson）和巴基·巴恩斯（Bucky Barnes）又回來一系列激動人心的冒險，將他們推向了極限。以Marvel Studios的原始系列《獵鷹與酷寒戰士》為基礎，Hot Toys很高興推出全新的Cosbaby系列產品，其中包括主角獵鷹和酷寒戰士。每個Cosbaby收藏品的高度約為10.5-11.5厘米（帶搖頭設計）。\n\n##### 時尚的Cosbaby重塑了獵鷹，他的漫畫靈感的服裝展開了機翼，為空襲做準備。仿生武裝的超級英雄酷寒戰士穿著新髮型和標誌性戰術服裝，正騎著摩托車搖擺。\n\n##### 用臭名昭著的英雄們開始您的《獵鷹與酷寒戰士》系列！\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/9Urtwte.jpg)\n\n##### Captain America’s best buddies, Sam Wilson and Bucky Barnes are back for a series of action-packed adventures that will push them to their limits. Based on Marvel Studios’ original series, The Falcon and The Winter Soldier, Hot Toys is excited to introduce the brand new Cosbaby line-up featuring the leading characters, Falcon and Winter Soldier. Each Cosbaby collectible measures approximately 10.5 - 11.5 cm tall with bobble-head design.\n\n##### The stylish Cosbaby has recreated Falcon and his comic book inspired outfit with the wings outspread, preparing for an air attack; and Winter Soldier, the bionic-armed super hero, is wearing a new hair style and signature tactical outfit, rocking up with a motorcycle.\n\n##### Kick start your Falcon and Winter Soldier collection with the infamous heroes!\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/2sbBqDJ.jpg)\n\n##### 尺寸：高10.5公分-11.5公分\n##### 預購價格：巴奇128港幣 約469新台幣 酷寒戰士138港幣 506新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年第二季-第三季\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7nnIs86.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/94v6jMR.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/0XEzG2r.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Hot Toys**](http://www.hottoys.com.hk/?fbclid=IwAR209xNQykEV9PgpXUxNqA0hV3lVOZmWez-jsVz-NYzzrhb9TQX22Rj7dlI)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/ogMckLU.jpg','','新聞','2021-03-29 17:33:00',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',26,7);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (501,'「挪威海怪 克拉肯（雷•哈利豪森）」豪華/普通版 35公分高雕像 Star Ace新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### **Star Ace**是追求卓越收藏品的國際收藏品牌，3月23日在[**官網**](http://starace.com.hk/?fbclid=IwAR3QYeyoKbN4jTfvS8qp-5Eka-2sN9cwkS5cZtdpJ-p-tI5orP5ywSNxMSA)發布旗下**SUPERVINYL SERIES系列**開放預購的 **「挪威海怪 克拉肯（雷•哈利豪森）」豪華/普通版 35公分高雕像**官方圖片與訊息，將於2021年第3季發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/dKF7nX5.jpg)\n\n##### 現可在[**野獸國**](https://www.beast-kingdom.com.tw/SalePage/Index/6897847)預購！\n\n##### 強大的挪威海怪是眾神派遣的巨大而可怕的海怪，以摧毀那些背叛了他們的凡人。也許是動畫師雷·哈里豪森（Ray Harryhausen）在定格動畫中的最大成就，挪威海怪是一個巨大的四臂生物，尾巴很長，臉龐恐怖。\n\n##### 雷·哈里豪森（Ray Harry Harryhausen）的挪威海怪（Kraken）的超級乙烯基雕像是Star Ace有史以來最大的創作。身高35厘米，全長54厘米，這個令人印象深刻的怪獸將是任何收藏品的絕佳展示品。傳統上由著名的Kaibutsuya生物商店的工匠雕刻而成，該雕像由柔軟的乙烯樹脂製成，並手繪以展現雕刻細節。\n\n##### 豪華版的挪威海怪附有一個樹脂製的海浪礁岩場景，上面刻有雕刻的海浪，還有一個被迫待救的公主。此擴展版本與底座的全長為64厘米。\n\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/TOb3TeZ.jpg)\n\n##### The mighty Kraken is a giant and fearsome sea monster sent by the gods to destroy mortals that have defied them. Perhaps Ray Harryhausen’s greatest achievement in stop-motion animation, the Kraken is a huge four-armed creature with a long tail and terrifying face.\n\n##### The Super Vinyl statue of Ray Harryhausen’s Kraken is the largest creation Star Ace has ever made. Standing 35cm tall and extending out a full 54 cm in length, this impressive monster will be an amazing display piece for any collection. Traditionally sculpted by the artisans of the famed creature shop of Kaibutsuya, the statue is made from soft vinyl and is hand-painted to bring out the details of the sculpt.\n\n##### The deluxe version of the Kraken comes with a polyresin diorama base with sculpted ocean waves and a manacled princess waiting to be rescued. This extended version measures a full 64cm in length with the base.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/W2MB009.jpg)\n##### 尺寸：高35公分｜寬30公分｜普通版長54公分 豪華版長64公分\n##### 預購價格：普通版11,250新台幣 豪華版12,600新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年第3季\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VGk9j1w.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7Jm2L22.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/YUxG5Tf.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Tt4wC6y.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/MrFv5Ct.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/p4j7UZ1.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/npRDxuL.jpg)\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Star Ace**](http://starace.com.hk/?fbclid=IwAR3QYeyoKbN4jTfvS8qp-5Eka-2sN9cwkS5cZtdpJ-p-tI5orP5ywSNxMSA)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/qlzDWyy.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/eaqq8mO.jpg','新聞','2021-03-29 17:34:52',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',23,7),(502,'《血源詛咒》「獵人」15公分可動人偶與武器包 figma Max Factory新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 日本代理商及製造商**Good Smile Company**，3月24日在[**官網**](https://www.goodsmile.info/)發布日本廠牌**Max Factory**旗下**figma系列**開放預購的 **《血源詛咒》「獵人」15公分可動人偶與武器包**官方圖片與訊息，將於2022年2月發售。\n\n##### 此款《血源詛咒》「獵人」為重新發行的版本，人物與武器包能夠分開或共同預購。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/zGZ2utE.jpg)\n\n##### 讓狩獵開始。\n\n##### 從PlayStation®4 RPG動作遊戲《血源詛咒》中可以重現「獵人」的figma！\n\n##### ·使用figma的光滑但合縫的關節，可以創建各種姿勢。\n##### ·柔性塑料用於重要區域，可以保持比例不變，而不會影響位置。\n##### ·鋸割刀和獵人手槍都包括在內，供獵人使用。\n##### ·可以像在遊戲中一樣將鋸切肉刀轉換成其擴展的切肉刀形式。\n##### ·包括一個關節的figma底座架，以各種姿勢展示figma。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wX6u1mV.jpg)\n\n##### “獵人必須狩獵。”\n\n##### 從PlayStation®4動作角色扮演遊戲《血源詛咒》中獲得了一個Figma PLUS套裝，其中包含各種不同的武器，可與您的Figma一起展示！\n\n##### ·套裝包括獵人短槍，獵人斧頭，陀螺鋸和路德維希的聖刃。\n##### ·獵人斧頭，陀螺鋸和路德維希的聖刃帶有可互換的零件，以變換後的形式顯示它們。\n##### ·包括特殊的附件，用於在figma獵人（另售）的背面顯示陀螺鋸和路德維希的聖刃。\n##### ·包括用來展示握著每種武器的Figma獵人的手部。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3uVTSEi.jpg)\n\n##### Let the Hunt Begin.\n\n##### From the PlayStation®4 action RPG \"Bloodborne\" comes a rerelease of the figma of the Hunter!\n\n##### · Using the smooth yet posable joints of figma, you can create a variety of poses.\n##### · A flexible plastic is used for important areas, allowing proportions to be kept without compromising posability.\n##### · Both the Saw Cleaver and Hunter Pistol are included as weapons for the Hunter to wield.\n##### · The Saw Cleaver can be transformed into its extended cleaver form just like in the game.\n##### · An articulated figma stand is included to display the figma in a variety of poses.\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6KLzB0o.jpg)\n\n\n##### \"A hunter must hunt.\"\n\n##### From the PlayStation®4 action RPG \"Bloodborne: The Old Hunters\" comes a figma PLUS set featuring a variety of different weapons to display with your figma!\n\n##### · The set includes the Hunter Blunderbuss, the Hunter Axe, the Whirligig Saw and Ludwig\'s Holy Blade.\n##### · The Hunter Axe, Whirligig Saw and Ludwig\'s Holy Blade come with interchangeable parts to display them in their transformed forms.\n##### · Special attachment parts are included to display the Whirligig Saw and Ludwig\'s Holy Blade on the back of figma Hunter (sold separately).\n##### · Hand parts to display figma Hunter holding each weapon are included.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/EIUUMuY.jpg)\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高15公分\n##### 預購價格：人物包85.99美元 約2,454新台幣 武器包37.99美元 約1,084新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2022年2月\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/FOMGcFf.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7ZWuush.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/m9B3LLP.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1TF6ZKi.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/CXUUmfS.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/nEW0xah.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/RdjDd8x.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NevFsgK.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/OmOhdpG.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NUVP53D.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/kwwzKfJ.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Good Smile Company**](https://www.goodsmile.info/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/UUJczPF.jpg','','新聞','2021-03-29 17:35:29',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',22,7),(503,'《蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻》「蝙蝠車」1/6比例珍藏品 Hot Toys新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 世界知名的收藏級1/6比例可動人偶的香港廠牌**Hot Toys**，今日在[**官網**](http://www.hottoys.com.hk/?fbclid=IwAR209xNQykEV9PgpXUxNqA0hV3lVOZmWez-jsVz-NYzzrhb9TQX22Rj7dlI)發布開放預購的 **《蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻》「蝙蝠車」1/6比例珍藏品 型號MMS596**官方圖片與訊息，將於2022年第三季-第四季發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/9JRvKix.jpg)\n\n##### 1/6比例的蝙蝠車收藏車輛特別具有以下特點：\n##### -蝙蝠俠中的真實和詳細的蝙蝠車開始\n##### -內部和機械設計上的高精度塗裝應用\n##### -約73cm長x 46cm寬x 27cm高\n##### -整個車身10個LED點亮點的車輛（白光，電池供電）\n##### -詳細的駕駛艙/車頂蓋面板結構\n##### -鉸接式折斷翻板\n##### -旋轉橡膠輪胎\n##### -尺寸適合1/6比例的蝙蝠俠收藏品公仔\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/GkZhbpu.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高27公分｜寬46公分｜長73公分\n##### 預購價格：3,900港幣 約14,310新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2022年第三季-第四季\n![](https://i.imgur.com/79YQGpN.jpg)\n\n\n##### he 1/6th scale Batmobile Collectible Vehicle specially features:\n##### - Authentically and detailed Batmobile in Batman Begins\n##### - Highly-accurate paint application on the interior and mechanical design\n##### - Approximately 73cm L x 46cm W x 27cm H\n##### - 10 LED light-up points throughout body of the vehicle (white light, battery operated)\n##### - Detailed cockpit/ roof opening panel structure\n##### - Articulated breaking flaps\n##### - Rotatable rubber tires\n##### - Sized to fit with 1/6th scale Batman Collectible Figure\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/O1lTQHE.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑