s.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/QGGx1XC.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/bkqTWlg.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ZWMg2uX.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/J0F2E12.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/i7Y0vb6.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/p6Hr8LY.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NLB1KNu.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/h2vuCWH.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**marvel.com**](https://www.marvel.com/articles/gear/shop-marvel-must-haves-baron-zemo)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/kK5lMpj.png','https://i.imgur.com/1qsb71h.png','新聞','2021-04-06 17:55:48',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',61,7),(538,'「KEEP ME IN YOUR HEART（幽靈版）」8吋高藝術雕像 Mighty Jaxx新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 總部位於新加坡的設計師品牌**Mighty Jaxx**，4月3日在[**官網**](https://mightyjaxx.rocks/)發布開放預購的 **「KEEP ME IN YOUR HEART（幽靈版）」8吋高藝術雕像**官方圖片與訊息，將於2021年9月發售。\n\n##### Mighty Jaxx這次再度推出藝術家馬特·貝利（Matt Bailey）的作品KEEP ME IN YOUR HEART黑色幽靈版，初始版本是全白的，黑色顛覆大眾對於骨頭的印象顏色，打火機的火也從白色的蠟燭火轉為更強烈的鮮紅色，整件作品傳達的概念更加劇烈。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/QvIqblM.jpg)\n\n\n##### 白天死了，晚上還活著，只有她有權喚醒他，她渴望著再次向他呼喚，每次回來時他的外表發生巨大變化，始終不會讓他感到煩惱，她代替她加入他的行列，吸一口氣，只想起了所有美好的事物和美好的事物。\n\n##### 她說：“把我留在你的心中，因為我永遠是你的。”\n\n##### 就像使火焰永恆燃燒的燃料一樣，她對它們的記憶使她繼續前進。\n\n##### 馬特·貝利（Matt Bailey）創作的KEEP ME IN YOUR HEART（幽靈版）是一件全黑的樹脂藝術收藏品，具有細膩的玩味，半透明的黑色骨架與啞光的黑色女性外形和高光澤度的裝飾物形成鮮明對比，這幅幻像作品是永恆的藝術品。\n\n##### 馬特·貝利大量藝術品中最常見的主題可能是情慾，馬特·貝利既性感又性感，而且通常很露骨，他不會迴避自己藝術中最先天和肉慾的人類慾望的表達，但他也以新穎而巧妙的方式做到了，與原版Keep Me In Your Heart類似，一位女士和她的愛人骨骼正處於親密的時刻，她的手處於特別有啟發性的姿勢，在此圖中使用了“口渴”一詞，這絕對不是在談論喝點酒的必要性！\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/GcjnWl1.jpg)\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高8吋\n##### 預購價格：269美元 約7,644新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年9月\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ZqMVPPn.jpg)\n\n##### Dead in the day, alive by night, only she has the power to wake him up. She calls out longingly to him once again, always unfazed by the drastic change in his appearance upon each return. She takes her place and joins him, taking a puff and reminiscing all the good things and the good things only.\n\n##### \"Keep me in your heart\" she says, \"for I am yours always.\"\n\n##### Like the fuel that keeps that flame burning eternally, her memories of them keeps her going.\n\n##### Keep Me in Your Heart by Matt Bailey (Spectre Edition) is an all-black polystone art collectible that features subtle material play. Contrasting the translucent black skeleton with the matte black female form and high gloss accents, this phantasmal piece is a timeless work of art.\n\n\n##### The most common theme in Matt Bailey\'s massive portfolio of artworks is probably lust. Sensual, sexual, and often pretty explicit, Matt Bailey is not one who would shy away from representing the most innate and carnal human desires in his art, but he also does so in fresh and clever ways. Similar to Keep Me In Your Heart, a lady and her lover skeleton is engaged in an intimate moment, with her hand in a particularly suggestive posture. The use of the word \"thirsty\" is on point in this illustration, and it\'s definitely not just talking about the need to sip some wine!\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wYTXE4h.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/nl2c00G.jpg)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/KCCljKA.jpg)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/I4Zy248.jpg)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/gX4L7iU.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Mighty Jaxx**](https://mightyjaxx.rocks/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/qyVJExf.png','https://i.imgur.com/NqWcVtz.png','新聞','2021-04-07 14:10:08',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',25,7),(539,'《風雲漫畫》「步驚雲」1/4比例全身雕像 ACME Studios新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 中國雕像品牌**ACME Studios**，3月31日發布開放預購的 **《風雲漫畫》「步驚雲」1/4比例全身雕像**官方圖片與訊息，現可以在[**XM Studios**](https://www.xm-studios.com/products/acme-studios-cloud-fung-wan.aspx)上進行預購，將於2022年第一季發售。\n\n##### 《風雲》是幻想式武俠故事，也是香港漫畫家馬榮成編繪的作品，故事圍繞在聶風（風）和步驚雲（雲）兩位主角身上。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/nRoG6yS.jpg)\n\n##### 故事發生在明朝時期，圍繞著兩位主角–聶風（風）和步驚雲（雲）–他們在早年學習武術，並成長為江湖的傳奇戰士，武術家社區（martial artists’ community），隨著故事的進展，新故事弧中會引入更多角色。\n\n##### 第一個故事是關於風和雲的起源的，當他們還是男孩的時候，他們的首領洪霸（征服者閣下）就被接納為武術家天下會（天下學會），他以一種秘密的動機對武術進行輔導，一位佛教先知曾告訴征服者，他將在“風和雲”的幫助下在江湖上台，當征服者達到其成就的頂峰時，預言的後半部分即被揭示：征服者的崛起歸因於風雲，但它們也注定會導致他的垮台，征服者的陰謀使風和雲相互對抗，故事的其餘部分講述了“風雲”從“天堂協會”逃脫後的歷險經歷。他們逐漸提高自己的技能，獲得強大的武器，與其他著名的江湖人物成為朋友，並滿足他們各自的浪漫興趣，風和雲最終實現了與鴻巴的對抗並擊敗了他，履行了預言。\n\n##### XM Studios很高興能從香港流行漫畫《風雲》中展示驚人的流行文化收藏品，這幅令人嘆為觀止的雕像是由ACME生產的，是藝術品，完美地捕捉了角色的細節和本質。\n\n##### ●由Acme Studio生產\n##### ●1：4比例\n##### ●限量版：500\n##### ●轉出：2個頭雕，2個右手手臂，龍頭髮光功能。\n##### ●預計產品尺寸（長x寬x高）：76x65x80cm\n##### ●預計出貨期：2022年第一季度\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Qw5XxbB.jpg)\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高80公分｜寬65公分｜長76公分\n##### 預購價格：21,99新加坡幣 約46,551新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2022年第一季\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/5jixRGx.jpg)\n\n\n##### The story is set in China during the Ming dynasty, and revolves around two protagonists – Nip Fung (Wind) and Bou Ging-wan (Cloud) – who learn martial arts in their early years and grow up to become legendary fighters in the jianghu (martial artists\' community). As the story progresses, more characters are introduced in new story arcs.\n\n##### The first story arc is about the origins of Wind and Cloud. When they were still boys, they were accepted into the martial arts clan Tin-ha-wui (Under Heaven Society) by its chief, Hung-ba (Lord Conqueror), who tutors them in martial arts for a secret motive. Conqueror was once told by a Buddhist prophet that he would rise to power in the jianghu with the help of \"Wind and Cloud\". When Conqueror reaches the pinnacle of his achievements, the second half of the prophecy is revealed: that Conqueror\'s rise is attributed to Wind and Cloud, but they are also destined to bring about his downfall. Conqueror plots to turn Wind and Cloud against each other. The rest of the story arc tells of the adventures of Wind and Cloud after they escape from Under Heaven Society. They gradually improve their skills, acquire powerful weapons, and befriend other prominent jianghu figures, as well as meeting their respective romantic interests. Wind and Cloud eventually return to confront Hung-ba and defeat him, fulfilling the prophecy.\n\n##### XM Studios is excited to present amazing Pop Culture Collectibles from the Popular Hong Kong Comics, 风云 (Fung Wan aka The Storm Riders). Produced by ACME, this breath taking statue is a work of Art, the details and essence of the character is captured perfectly.\n\n##### ●Produced by Acme Studio\n##### ●1:4 Scale\n##### ●Limited Edition: 500\n##### ●Switch-Outs: 2 Headsculpt, 2 Right hand switchout,Light up features at the Dragon\'s head.\n##### ●Est Product Size (LxBxHt): 76x65x80cm\n##### ●Est Shipping out period: Q1 2022\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/DOPQVFu.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/DXQDzk8.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SMXkLgE.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/aoQiNbg.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/px0UfW4.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/uX1qXcZ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/GaqIsTC.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/2NXBPAL.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/MdgZ54H.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/lmttxf3.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/XLqSAJ1.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6pNfWaV.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**XM Studios**](https://www.xm-studios.com/products/acme-studios-cloud-fung-wan.aspx)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/1RYRVxS.png','https://i.imgur.com/QMYOyiE.png','新聞','2021-04-07 14:10:50',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',21,7),(540,'《拿破崙炸藥》「拿破崙」 The Loyal Subjects新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### The Loyal Subjects是驅動藝術收藏品的市場領導者之一，並專門製造Q版尺寸的高品質玩具，近日發布旗下**BST AXN 5吋系列**開放預購的 ****官方圖片與訊息，現可在[target](https://www.target.com/p/napoleon-napoleon-dynamite-bst-axn-5-34-action-figure/-/A-81640397#lnk=sametab)預購。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/gRrblze.png)\n\n\n##### 《拿破崙炸藥》講述高中生拿破崙在校園與生活發生的趣事，怪咖之間的互助表現其實不亞於校園校花校草的一舉一動，儘管這部是魯蛇都必須朝聖的電影，不過《拿破崙炸藥》的票房表現一點也不魯蛇，以40萬美金的電影預算拿到超過1500萬美金的誇張票房，就像在周遭出現的故事儼然成為美國著名電影。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ghFvJnB.png)\n\n##### 拿破崙身穿印有Endurance字樣的T恤、藍色牛仔褲及黑色長靴，重現劇中的褐色捲髮和大眼鏡，可動程度可以讓你擺出各式「怪咖」動作，附上隨身聽及1對替換手。\n\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/TyFC3nn.png)\n\n##### 尺寸：高5吋\n##### 預購價格：15.99美元 約454新台幣\n##### 發售日期：未公布\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/39s0TU8.png)\n##### 圖片來源：[target](https://www.target.com/p/napoleon-napoleon-dynamite-bst-axn-5-34-action-figure/-/A-81640397#lnk=sametab)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/w4NJZGG.jpg','','新聞','2021-04-07 14:11:13',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',32,7),(541,'《哥吉拉 II 怪獸之王》「拉頓」25公分高PVC完成品 X-PLUS新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 日本X-PLUS公司，4月5日在[**官網**](https://us.ric-toy.com/psdr08r-wldna.html)發布開放預購的 **《哥吉拉 II 怪獸之王》「拉頓」25公分高PVC完成品**官方圖片與訊息，由PVC材料進行製作，將於2021年8月發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/KYPYSyu.jpg)\n\n\n##### 2019年發行的好萊塢版哥斯拉的拉頓（2019）登陸TOHO Large Kaiju系列！\n##### 繼哥斯拉（2019）之後，拉頓（2019）終於出現在TOHO Large Kaiju系列中！\n\n##### 這個版本的拉頓具有大角度的機翼和動感十足的姿勢，使您感覺隨時可以俯伏。\n##### 該模型經過精心