.com/xCfUeQp.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/B1sR8ji.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/rnjy5J1.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/pIloxKc.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/vHagU4D.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BZ2iOK1.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/xacOuqt.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/UaSJqOR.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/IUmEbbX.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/r1mtsxi.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/YUpoJhA.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/A6YAGpE.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/G6aYPVq.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/FQTgFvJ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SIyUjRx.jpg)\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**XM Studios**](https://www.xm-studios.com/pages/default.aspx)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/wdDL5wD.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/uahv4OU.jpg','新聞','2021-04-09 11:19:06',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',39,7),(553,'《Superman - The Mechanical Monsters (1941)》「3.75吋人物豪華場景盒」Mezco Toyz新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 擅長製造恐怖角色的美式品牌**Mezco Toyz**，4月7日在[**官網**](https://www.mezcotoyz.com/)發布旗下**5 Points廠牌**開放預購的 **《Superman - The Mechanical Monsters (1941)》「3.75吋人物豪華場景盒」**官方圖片與訊息，將於2021年9月-11月發售。\n\n\n##### 3.75吋人物盒裝場景盒內有：超人、克拉克(記者版超人)、露易絲·蓮恩、機械怪獸5號，筆記本、電話亭、2對替換超人手臂、2對替換機械怪獸手臂、1個用於機械怪獸的螺旋槳附件、2個機械怪物的火焰效果、4個展示底座\n\n##### 5 Points是Mezco對過去明確的可動人物的升級，這些高度詳細，可擺放的動作人物具有流行文化中最熟悉的面孔，包括新老面孔。\n\n##### 5 Points Superman - The Mechanical Monsters (1941)：3.75吋人物豪華場景盒包裝在易於收藏的盒子中，專為收藏家而設計。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Cy5jCsU.jpg)\n\n\n##### 在天空中，看：它是一隻鳥，這是一架飛機，是超人！\n\n##### 5 Points Superman - The Mechanical Monsters (1941)：3.75吋人物豪華場景盒，靈感來自1940年代動畫短片《The Mechanical Monsters》。\n\n##### 比超速的子彈更快，比機車更強大，能夠跳的比建築物還高，這套超人豪華盒裝套裝包含3個人物，一個巨型射擊機器人，一個快速更換電話亭以及多層三層樓環境立體模型！\n\n##### 露易絲·蓮恩小姐，這是一個故事嗎？借助快速更改功能，克拉克·肯特進入電話亭，超人出現了！\n\n##### 組裝完成後，復古劇場立體模型會在一側創建守衛良好的珠寶屋店面，反面則是《瘋狂科學家》實驗室的兩層樓立體模型，該實驗室配有一扇可打開的吊橋門，以及一排機械怪獸，在偽造怪獸的下方設有一個秘密的火山洞穴。 \n\n \n\n##### 5 Points Superman - The Mechanical Monsters (1941)：3.75吋人物豪華場景盒包括：\n##### 超人–來自另一個星球的奇怪訪客，其力量遠遠超過了凡人，超人配有兩對可替換的手臂，以進行動態擺姿勢和柔軟的模壓披風。\n##### 克拉克·肯特–超人的另一個自我，克拉克隱瞞了他作為《每日星球》溫和派記者的英雄身份，克拉克配有可攜帶物品\n##### 露易絲·蓮恩–《每日星球》的頑強調查記者，露易絲堅強、果斷，能夠在危險情況下處理自己，露易絲帶有一個小筆記本配件，可以記錄下她的下一個大新聞。\n##### 機械怪獸5號–由瘋狂科學家創建的一小撮邪惡機器人，用以竊取金錢和珠寶，這些機械怪獸是犯罪的不可阻擋的犯罪者。這種超大型機器具有兩對可替換的手臂，可擺動態姿勢，一個可替換的螺旋槳附在脖子上，機身後部有一個關節式隔層，可拆卸的火焰特效附在其眼睛上。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hEldlKz.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高3.75吋\n##### 預購價格：90美元 約2,561新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年9月-11月\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/otXWq21.jpg)\n\n##### Up in the sky, look: it\'s a bird. It\'s a plane. It\'s Superman!\n\n##### 5 Points present – Superman (1941): Deluxe Boxed Set, inspired by the 1940s animated short The Mechanical Monsters.\n\n##### Faster than a speeding bullet, more powerful than a locomotive, able to leap tall buildings in a single bound - this Superman deluxe boxed set contains 3 figures, a giant fire shooting robot, a quick-change phone booth, and multi-level, triple environment diorama!\n\n##### How’s this for a story, Miss Lane? Clark Kent goes into the phone booth and Superman comes out thanks to the quick-change feature!\n\n##### Once assembled, the retro play set diorama creates the well-guarded House of Jewels storefront on one side, and a two-story diorama of The Mad Scientist’s lab on the reverse side. The lab comes complete with a drawbridge door that opens and rows of Mechanical Monsters with a secret volcanic cavern below where the monsters are forged. \n\n \n\n##### THE 5 POINTS SUPERMAN – THE MECHANICAL MONSTERS (1941): DELUXE BOXED SET INCLUDES:\n##### ●Superman – Strange visitor from another planet with powers far beyond those of mortal men. Superman comes with two pairs of interchangeable arms for dynamic posing and a soft molded cape.\n##### ●Clark Kent – Superman’s alter ego, Clark, conceals his heroic identity as a mild-mannered reporter for The Daily Planet. Clark comes with a holdable\n##### ●Lois Lane – A tenacious investigative reporter at the Daily Planet. Strong, assertive, and able to handle herself in dangerous situations, Lois comes with a small notebook accessory to document her next big scoop.\n##### ●Mechanical Monster Number 5 – A small army of evil robots created by The Mad Scientist to steal money and jewels, the Mechanical Monsters were unstoppable perpetrators of crime. This oversized machine of mayhem comes with two pairs of interchangeable arms for dynamic posing, an interchange propeller that attaches to the neck, a hinged compartment on the back of its body, and removable flame FX that attach to its eyes.\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/KOfoWpv.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/e0FMoL8.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/HChTT4q.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/WROHBDJ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/TALUHAn.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ab1dNqV.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VjYv58c.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ov7Uluq.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/33dcu1O.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Mezco Toyz**](https://www.mezcotoyz.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/hZQrqaU.jpg','','新聞','2021-04-09 11:19:42',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',173,7),(554,'《DC漫畫》「哈莉·奎茵和小丑」35公分收藏雕像 Sideshow Collectibles新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 美國廠牌製造商同時也是經銷商的**Sideshow Collectibles**，近日在[**官網**](https://www.sideshow.com/)發布開放預購的 **《DC漫畫》「哈莉·奎茵和小丑」35公分收藏雕像**官方圖片與訊息，將於2022年5月-7月發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/kAQP7hV.jpg)\n\n\n##### “讓我們嘗試一些新材料。”\n\n##### Sideshow展示了Harley Quinn and The Joker Diorama，將它們引入DC漫畫收藏品陣容。\n\n##### 當談到高譚的小丑表演時，Mistah J和他最好的女孩哈莉總是確保笑話到位-即使是從大砲中射出來的！哈莉·奎茵和小丑的立體模型的身高分別為14吋和11吋，這兩隻犯罪的愛情鴛鴦正準備讓他們行動起來，坐在紫色和橙色的加農炮底座上，哈莉·奎茵舉行比賽，這將使犯罪王子小丑升空，而在槍管內，小丑不禁微笑，因為他繪製了下一個惡作劇給蝙蝠俠。 \n\n##### 哈莉·奎茵和小丑樹脂立體模型被完全雕刻，幾乎與個性一起爆炸（這不僅是因為哈雷即將點燃保險絲），受到經典漫畫作品的啟發，哈莉·奎茵和小丑製作了色彩繽紛，淡淡的二重奏，哈莉身著標誌性的紅色和黑色小丑服裝，帶有白色調，並帶有白色調，小丑服裝的紫色套裝，橙色正裝襯衫和藍色領帶可以在他從大砲中凝視時看到，底座雕刻有逼真的木質紋理，並飾有“Ha Ha Ha”文字圖案，隱藏在蝙蝠俠盜賊畫廊中這些粉絲最愛下方的圓形底座中的是一個隱藏的蝙蝠符號，這證明了當發生麻煩時，高譚的披肩永遠都不會落後。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/vKq1LME.jpg)\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高35.5公分｜寬27.9公分｜長15.2公分\n##### 預購價格：530美元 約15,091新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2022年5月-7月\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/EOJaMLb.jpg)\n\n\n##### “Let’s try some new material.”\n\n##### Sideshow presents the Harley Quinn and The Joker Diorama, launching into your lineup of DC Comics collectibles.\n\n##### When it comes to clowning around in Gotham, Mistah J and his best girl Harley always make sure that the joke lands- even when it’s shot out of a cannon! The Harley Quinn and The Joker Diorama measures 14” tall and 11” wide as the two criminal lovebirds prepare to take their partner act up a notch. Sitting on a purple and orange colored cannon base, Harley Quinn holds the match that will send the Clown Prince of Crime sky-high, while inside the barrel, The Joker can’t help but smile as he plots the punchline to his next prank on Batman. \n\n##### The polyresin Harley Quinn and The Joker Diorama is fully sculpted, practically exploding with personality (and that’s not just because Harley’s about to light the fuse). Inspired by their classic comic book appearances, Harley Quinn and The Joker make a colorful, clownish duo. Harley wears her iconic two-toned red and black jester costume with white accents, and The Joker’s purple suit, orange dress shirt, and blue necktie can be seen as he peers out of the cannon. The base is sculpted with realistic wood-like textures and is patterned with “Ha Ha Ha” text. A hidden Bat-symbol is weathered into the circular pedestal below these fan-favorites in the Batman Rogues Gallery, proving that Gotham’s Caped Crusader is never far behind when trouble strikes.\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4ajO6Sv.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/LJCJkDR.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qe8VBTf.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/AkDQPNN.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/B3DJlN0.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/nw6qbaL.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/260Sukm.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Jc85Phk.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/pr7aQmo.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/tN1oSHP.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ZheTnna.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SFhXyGp.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/tPKLHQE.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/e7L8Joa.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ZSrsXdD.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/IkvnyIC.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Sideshow Collectibles**](https://www.sideshow.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/x9VHbDm.png','https://i.imgur.com/EfyZCYl.jpg','新聞','2021-04-09 11:20:14',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',56,7),(555,'《Marvel 英雄大亂鬥》「死侍」1/3比例全身雕像 Premium Collectibles Studio(PCS)新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### Premium Collectibles Studio(PCS)雕像品牌與世界各地藝術家合作，並對雕像有頑固的品質要求，今日發布 **《Marvel 英雄大亂鬥》「死侍」1/3比例全身雕像**官方圖片與訊息，並在太平洋時間4月15日下午12點至下午3點在[**Sideshow Collectibles**](https://www.sideshow.com/)開始預購。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/cIsZ8Sw.jpg)\n\n\n##### “我會在這裡殺害一些雞隻！我的意思是，我還是會殺了你，但即使是像我這樣英俊的變種人也需要早餐！”\n\n##### Sideshow和PCS展示了死侍1：3比例雕像，靈感來自韋韋德·威爾森（Wade Wilson）的瘋狂行為，他出現在熱門遊戲Marvel 英雄大亂鬥。\n\n##### 該Deadpool 1：3比例的雕像與toppings at a taco truck相比，雕像有更多的展示選項，所以你終於可以在你不那麼秘密的死侍聖地中擁有一個耀眼的核心，在標準的銀色平台底座上，死侍的高度為24吋，隨時可以與競技場上的其他冠軍進行對接。一些英雄為榮耀或正義而戰-但韋德·威爾森的動機無非就是他最喜歡的獨角獸Uni，當死侍站起來守衛他的超大型超酷獨角獸展示底座時，這款Marvel收藏品的高度高達38吋，寬12吋。完整的底座包括一個旋轉的Uni人物形象，有點亮功能和可移動的附著標誌，以嚇所有卑鄙的小偷。\n。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/8sdeSMd.jpg)\n\n##### 令人難以置信的精細死侍1：3比例雕像被雕刻完成，以他所有的Marvel Gamerverse榮耀與他標誌性的紅色和黑色服裝一起用嘴捕捉水星，借助兩個獨特的頭雕和兩種不同的武器搭載，收藏家可以重新生成其死侍顯示具有無數種配置可能性，該雕像既包括一個傻笑，自信的臉龐，又有強烈的動作，都為你的觀賞樂趣而加分，韋德裝備了一對他的假名簽名片和一把紅色槍，上面塗著有趣的提醒，提醒他們應該以哪種方式指向壞人，呵呵，該人物還包括在他的背上的護套，上面帶有可移動的劍柄，具體取決於您所展示的武器，另外還有一對袖扣，可讓您在展櫃內炫耀死侍的（斷頭）多餘的雙手-這些傢伙想到了一切！\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/FX66aRy.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高38吋｜寬12吋\n##### 預購價格：1,275美元 約36,307新台幣\n##### 發售日期：未公布\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4YCrp8k.jpg)\n\n##### “I’d kill for some chimichangas up in here! I mean, I’ll kill you anyway, but even a handsome mutant like me needs breakfast!”\n\n##### Sideshow and PCS present the Deadpool 1:3 Scale Statue, inspired by the insanity of Wade Wilson as he appears in the hit game Marvel Contest of Champions.\n\n##### The Deadpool 1:3 Scale Statue comes with more display options than toppings at a taco truck so you can finally have a shining centerpiece to your not-so-secret Deadpool shrine. On the standard silver platform base, Deadpool measures 24” tall, ready to kick butt against other Champions in the arena. Some heroes battle for glory, or justice- but Wade Wilson’s motivation is none other than his favorite unicorn, Uni. When Deadpool stands guarding his ultra-mega-awesome unicorn showcase base, this Marvel collectible measures a whopping 38” tall and 12” wide. The full base includes a rotating Uni figure, light-up features, and removable cling signs to scare off any dastardly thieves.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/vwxgPby.jpg)\n\n##### The unbelievably detailed Deadpool 1:3 Scale Statue is fully sculpted to capture the Merc with a Mouth in all of his Marvel Gamerverse glory, complete with his iconic red and black costume. With two unique portraits and two different weapons loadouts, collectors can regenerate their Deadpool display with countless possibilities for configuration. The statue includes both a smirking, confident face and an intense action portrait, both masked for your viewing pleasure. Wade comes armed with a pair of his signature katanas and a pair of red guns graffitied with fun reminders about which way they should be pointed- towards the bad guys, duh. The figure also includes a sheath on his back with removable sword hilts depending on which weapons you have displayed. An additional pair of cuff holders allows you to show off Deadpool’s (severed) extra hands inside the showcase- these guys thought of everything!\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Q5K2Ea7.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/etpZrKg.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1RIfogx.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SvaHckO.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3J0L2IP.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/E5zS5Dd.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ixQh8l4.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VWugSY7.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/OoGgH8U.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/bIAxFwg.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/0riuzRZ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/rN879eA.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Lx17Log.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/bUMp2eo.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/OcDWrHl.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/65ULY6X.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wtEKI1f.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SZORDFC.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ETuPaFm.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/c3DXiIf.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hXbUiWK.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/X72kBl9.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Iieu7bS.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wWwmAoL.jpg)\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/bL2Cnj3.jpg)\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/k5prmIb.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/I8kyWtp.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qEkeOLA.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/58YpJ3p.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4mMoGES.jpg)\n\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/9uNFQ6h.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/10Su85V.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/iZ5HqOJ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/8585kT8.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Sideshow Collectibles**](https://www.sideshow.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/Sg4OlRx.png','https://i.imgur.com/rzcij5w.jpg','新聞','2021-04-12 05:02:09',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',30,7),(556,'《黑暗騎士：黎明昇起》「瑟琳娜·凱爾 貓女」1/3比例全身雕像 JND Studios新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 致力打造品質獨一無二的韓國雕像品牌**JND Studios**，4月9日發布在[**官網**](https://jndstudios.co.kr/home)開放預購的 **《黑暗騎士：黎明昇起》「瑟琳娜·凱爾 貓女」1/3比例全身雕像**官方圖片與訊息，將於2022年第一季-第二季發售。\n\n##### JND Studios的前三個項目：希斯版小丑、瓦昆版小丑、神力女超人，都將飾演演員的神情與身材都完美複製，採用玻璃眼、髮根，讓你所感覺不到的細節更加逼真以帶動整體的寫實度。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/131TI8V.jpg)\n\n\n##### 《黑暗騎士：黎明昇起》的2021年第一款產品和JND Studios的第四個項目是瑟琳娜·凱爾 貓女。\n\n##### 由美麗的安·海瑟薇飾演的瑟琳娜·凱爾 貓女是一個令人著迷的角色，裡面的人物角色截然不同。 \n\n##### 她是個反派人物，在角色結束時就變成了英雄。\n\n##### 與往常一樣，JND Studios創作的作品將使收藏家想起他們自己的電影《黑暗騎士：黎明昇起》的電影體驗，並將聚光燈指向美麗的蛇蠍美人。 \n\n##### JND的瑟琳娜·凱爾由李秀英（Soyoung Lee）重塑而成，她在2020年的神力女超女中獲得了很多讚譽。 \n\n##### 秀英似乎再次提高了自己的水平，以我們尚未見到的相似性來設計和建造瑟琳娜·凱爾。\n\n##### JND Studios繼續致力於為世界各地的雕像收藏家和電影迷創造不可替代的產品。正如Kojun經常說的那樣， \n\n##### “這只是原型。我們將努力工作，以使生產不會令信任我們的收藏家失望。\n\n\n\n##### 規格：\n##### ●雕像高度：約26英寸[H：65cm W：31cm D：31cm]\n##### ●1個主要雕像，帶有玻璃眼，紮根的頭髮和高品質的蝙蝠俠頭套，護目鏡，手槍，2個替換手臂\n##### ●1個特別設計的底座\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1NK9cvm.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高65公分｜寬31公分｜長31公分\n##### 預購價格：1,999美元 約56,914新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2022年第一季-第二季\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/It4TZqz.jpg)\n\n##### The first product of 2021 and the 4th project by JND Studios is Selina Kyle, Catwoman, from The Dark Knight Rises.\n\n##### Selina Kyle, played by the beautiful Anne Hathaway, is an intriguing character with very contrasting personas within. \n\n##### She’s a villain who transforms into a hero by the end of her character arc.\n\n##### As always, JND Studios has created a piece in a way that will remind collectors of their own cinematic experience of The Dark Knight Rises and point the spot light on the beautiful femme fatale. \n\n##### JND’s Selina Kyle was recreated by none other than Soyoung Lee, who received much accolade for her rendition of Wonder Woman in 2020. \n\n##### Soyoung seemed to have stepped up her game yet again, to design and build the Selina Kyle with likeness we have yet to see.\n\n##### JND Studios continues the endeavor to create products irreplaceable for statue collectors and film fans everywhere. And as Kojun always says, \n\n##### “This is only the prototype. We will work hard, so that production will not disappoint the collectors who have put their trust in us.\n\n\n\n##### Specifications:\n\n##### Statue height: approximately 26 inches [H:65cm W:31cm D:31cm]\n\n##### One (1) main piece statue with glass eye, rooted hair, and high quality Batman cowl, goggles, hand gun, (2) swappable arm variations\n\n##### One (1) specially designed base\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/MGSFKAh.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/rS1IgfE.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3rrwXXw.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/dp5rc15.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/zwxm85V.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/iUshbV8.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/PLYGtbG.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/V8qubSa.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/vm7m29M.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Fig1WZL.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Ux7opdb.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/b33nnQm.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Aeilwso.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/2aPGECx.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mP8CU8S.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ykGer0t.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Qm2pobD.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**JND Studios粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/jndstudioscollectibles/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/BUvGVN1.png','https://i.imgur.com/7O66Lwm.jpg','新聞','2021-04-12 09:10:23',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',38,7),(557,'《禁毒衛士》「Toxie 放射性紅色憤怒」7吋可動人偶 SUPER7新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 專製3.75吋可動人偶的美國廠牌**SUPER7**，4月7日在[**官網**](https://super7.com/?fbclid=IwAR2Ha_LUnCX7_H0MfBtgCQZI6Dq_tLlpIWri2oYb_UpDSkqEv8yayHkLZOw)發布開放預購的 **《禁毒衛士》「Toxie 放射性紅色憤怒」7吋可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，將於2022年第一季發售。\n\n##### Toxie 放射性紅色憤怒採用夜光塗料和變色塗料，在陽光下，Toxie會出現看似憤怒的紅色放射性顏色，配件的拖把上帶有美國國旗，還有盾牌與替換頭雕，高7吋，預購價格為55美元。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Fs6CVqE.jpg)\n\n\n##### 是Toxie，就像您從未見過他一樣！借助半透明的綠色夜光注射劑和UV反應性變色塗料，這是終極選擇！圖將具有三種不同的外觀，就好像Toxie在應對氣候變化一樣！他的標準外觀是明亮的霓虹燈漆，在陽光下，毒藥幾乎會立即變成憤怒的紅色！在黑暗中，他會發出險惡的綠色！\n\n##### Toxie 放射性紅色憤怒終極版！人物配備了可替換的頭雕和配件，包括可掛手榴彈的皮帶，帶夾扣式旗幟的拖把以及半透明的橙色《禁毒衛士》品牌盾牌，您的終極目標！圖將包裝在豪華的滑套式盒子中，預計將於2022年第一季發貨。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/s5HKrZM.jpg)\n\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高7吋\n##### 預購價格：55美元 約1,565新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2022年第一季\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VabPLTE.jpg)\n##### It’s Toxie, like you’ve never seen him before! With translucent green glow-in-the-dark injection and UV reactive color changing paint, this ULTIMATES! figure will have three different looks, as if Toxie is reacting to climate change! His standard appearance features bright neon paint, and in sunlight, Toxie will almost instantly change to an angry red! In the dark, he will glow a menacing green!\n\n##### The Radioactive Red Rage Toxic Crusader ULTIMATES! figure comes with interchangeable heads and accessories, including a belt with grenades, a mop with a clip-on flag, and a translucent orange Toxic Crusaders branded shield. Your ULTIMATES! figure will come packaged in a deluxe slip-case style box, and is expected to ship Q1 2022.\n![](https://i.imgur.com/EOARcD8.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mEm2JWH.jpg)\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**SUPER7**](https://preorder.super7store.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/Q9ga8JI.jpg','','新聞','2021-04-12 09:35:30',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',24,7),(558,'《芙蓉仙子》「Pizzazz」、「Jem」3.75吋可動人偶 SUPER7新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 專製3.75吋可動人偶的美國廠牌**SUPER7**，4月7日在[**官網**](https://super7.com/?fbclid=IwAR2Ha_LUnCX7_H0MfBtgCQZI6Dq_tLlpIWri2oYb_UpDSkqEv8yayHkLZOw)發布開放預購的 **《芙蓉仙子》「Pizzazz」、「Jem」3.75吋可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，將於2021年6月發售。\n\n##### 《芙蓉仙子（Jem and the Holograms）》動畫講述傑里卡的父親在過世前留給他一台擁有全息投影的電腦Synergy，讓他能夠化身為Jem，與好友組成樂團Jem and the Holograms，但光鮮亮麗的身分下為他們帶來了不少麻煩。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/q6kP7Dc.jpg)\n\n##### 尺寸：高3.75吋75吋\n##### 預購價格：單款18美元 約512新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年6月\n\n##### Pizzazz\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Wvxvc5o.jpg)\n##### 您可以立即開始聚會，Pizzazz在這裡！Misfits主唱的這個3.75吋關節式可動人物配有她的吉他和卡片，隨時可以晃動，並給Holograms帶來麻煩！一直在尋找風頭的Pizzazz完全會成為你的可動系列的一部分-別叫她的Phyllis，否則她會完全迷失它！\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/g3wTiVH.jpg)\n\n##### You can start the party now, Pizzazz is here! This 3.75” articulated ReAction figure of the lead singer of the Misfits comes with her guitar and a holographic cardback, ready to rock and cause some trouble for the Holograms! Always looking for the limelight, Pizzazz would be totally stoked to be a part of your ReAction collection- just DON’T call her Phyllis, or she’ll totally lose it!\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BwOBZpl.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### Jem\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3g8kyWb.jpg)\n##### 電腦Synergy的力量已將傑里卡·本頓（Jerrica Benton）轉變成神話般的流行歌星Jem，Holograms的主唱的這個3.75吋關節式可動人物隨她的麥克風一起提供，並直接出現在您80年代夢想的全息卡片上。如果不把這個Jem的ReAction人物放在您的收藏中，那真是太離譜了！\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BX7cqZ7.png)\n\n##### The power of Synergy has transformed Jerrica Benton into the totally fabulous popstar Jem. This 3.75” articulated ReAction figure of the lead singer of the Holograms comes with her microphone, and is on a holographic cardback straight out of your 80s dreams. Not putting this ReAction figure of Jem in the spotlight of your collection would be truly outrageous!\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/0DjRTCR.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**SUPER7**](https://preorder.super7store.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/BBiEQiu.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/L9GHVLW.jpg','新聞','2021-04-12 10:08:13',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',27,7),(559,'眼中只有披薩《忍者龜1987》「終極披薩怪」7吋可動人偶 NECA新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### NECA(國家娛樂收藏品協會)，4月9日發布開放預購的 **《忍者龜1987》「終極披薩怪」7吋可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，現在可以在[**The NECA Store**](https://thenecastore.com/)預購。\n\n##### 《忍者龜1987》「終極披薩怪」7吋可動人偶以多重墨線表現出動畫感，附上盒裝披薩、遠端控制器、小披薩怪，預購價格為34.99美元。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6PX3oE0.jpg)\n\n\n##### 基於經典的1980年代《忍者神龜》卡通系列！在意外暴露於放射性軟泥之後，四隻普通的家庭寵物變成了一群狡猾的，喜歡比薩餅，反派切丁的青少年爬行動物！\n##### 無論是面對兇猛的敵人還是要拯救人類免於滅絕，在他們的老師的指導下，這些“半殼英雄”始終可以直接衝出下水道的行動！\n\n##### 比薩怪獸來自Dimension X，是擊敗海龜的計劃的一部分，該計劃最終失敗了，需要雙方共同擊敗外來威脅，這款《忍者龜1987》終極披薩怪高聳於9吋高的海龜之上，並包括其青少年披薩怪形式，盒裝比薩餅和一個遠程控制裝置，具有友善收藏家的特徵。\n##### 窗盒包裝。\n\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/9cYDu5q.jpg)\n\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高7吋\n##### 預購價格：34.99美元 約995新台幣\n##### 發售日期：未公布\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Cr3hJIb.jpg)\n\n##### Based on the classic 1980s Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles cartoon series! After being accidentally exposed to radioactive ooze, four ordinary household pets are transformed into a band of wisecracking, pizza-loving, villain-dicing adolescent reptiles!\n##### Whether it\'s facing fierce enemies or saving humanity from near extinction, with the guidance of their Sensei, these Heroes in a Half Shell are always ready for straight outta the sewer action!\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/AhFJCxl.jpg)\n\n##### The Pizza Monsters come from Dimension X, and are part of a plot to defeat the Turtles which ultimately fails and requires both sides to team up to defeat the alien threat. This Ultimate Pizza Monster towers over the Turtles at 9\" tall, and includes its juvenile Pizza Monster form, pizza in box, and a remote control device. Comes in collector-friendly\n##### Window box packaging.\n![](https://i.imgur.com/gSd0q8M.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/AoseV69.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BDGZzAd.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/FMOtQPR.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/fhxWeKL.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/rJUpQGG.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**The NECA Store**](https://thenecastore.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/5teteUl.png','https://i.imgur.com/fa4Ayyq.jpg','新聞','2021-04-12 10:47:31',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',43,7),(560,'《忍者蝙蝠俠》「忍者蝙蝠俠2.0」普通/豪華版 1/6比例可動人偶 Star Ace新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### **Star Ace**是追求卓越收藏品的國際收藏品牌，近日發布開放預購的 **《忍者蝙蝠俠》「忍者蝙蝠俠2.0」普通/豪華版 1/6比例可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，現在可以在[**Sideshow Collectibles**](https://www.sideshow.com/)進行預購，將於2021年9月-11月發售。\n\n\n##### 《忍者蝙蝠俠》「忍者蝙蝠俠2.0」普通/豪華版 1/6比例可動人偶，蝙蝠俠身穿武士盔甲、高跟涼鞋，頭盔連接白色毛髮，還有綁上麻繩，配件附上帶刀鞘的武士刀、蝙蝠鏢、匕首、替換手、底座，高29.9公分，豪華版多普通版一隻武士馬，武士馬可以另外購買，預購價格為普通版270美元，豪華版340美元，單售武士馬149美元。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/PcIgl2T.jpg)\n\n\n##### 在DC動畫電影《忍者蝙蝠俠》中，蝙蝠俠以及他的一些盟友和對手被趕回了中世紀的日本，黑暗騎士採用忍者的武器和方法擊敗了現在是封建領主的小丑和其他惡棍，穿上特殊的蝙蝠武士裝甲，蝙蝠俠進入與小丑的最後一戰。\n\n##### 這款來自蝙蝠俠忍者的新1/6人物的特徵是，蝙蝠俠身著武士裝甲，配以帶有蝙蝠符號和高跟涼鞋的紅色戰袍，蝙蝠俠在與敵人戰鬥時，頭雕表情是戰鬥中的大吼，他配備了兩個武士刀，兩個蝙蝠鏢和兩個忍者匕首。\n\n##### “CoolToys”武士馬是Star Ace的忍者蝙蝠俠武士版本的完美搭配。\n\n##### 這匹黑色的戰馬到處都有雕刻精美的馬毛細節，並為鬃毛和尾巴扎了根頭髮，它配備有正宗的中世紀日本馬鞍，馬鞍和大頭釘，為紫色、橙色和黑色，蝙蝠圖案附著在面罩的側面，馬腿鎧甲的穗狀釘與蝙蝠俠武士的前臂鎧甲相搭配。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ZML1AJO.jpg)\n\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高29.9公分\n##### 預購價格：普通版270美元 約7,679新台幣 \n##### 豪華版340美元 約9,670新台幣 \n##### 單售武士馬149美元 約4,237新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年9月-11月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/r8UYGsH.jpg)\n\n##### In the animated DC film Batman Ninja, Batman, along with several of his allies and adversaries, are thrust back in time to medieval Japan. The Dark Knight takes on the weapons and methods of the ninja to defeat Joker and his other villains, who are now feudal lords. Donning special Bat-Samurai armor, Batman rides into the final battle against Joker.\n\n##### This new 1/6 figure from Batman Ninja features Batman in his ceremonial samurai armor complete with a red tabard with the bat-symbol and high sandals. The head sculpt features Batman in mid-battle yell as he rides into battle with his foes.  He’s outfitted with two katana, two batarangs, and two ninja daggers (Kunai).\n\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/g0xlhWo.jpg)\n\n##### The “CoolToys” Samurai horse is the perfect companion for Star Ace’s Batman Ninja Samurai version.\n\n##### This black war horse has finely sculpted horsehair detail all over and has rooted hair for the mane and tail. It is outfitted with authentic medieval Japanese saddle, stirrups and tack in purple, orange and black.  Bat-medallions are attached to the sides of the face mask and the horse leg armor features spikes to match the forearm armor of Batman Samurai.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hOcLD4m.jpg)\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/E1lrWbH.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/G5Rdnqf.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7BZuMi9.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/QarVjMO.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4QXmhqT.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/WfhZ14l.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/cEVNMRi.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/XkpSO9t.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/RCz9NYQ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mngm8iT.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/HFgkmn6.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/frZrQ2Q.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/32iEDf0.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/y1YaHlb.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/tI9ieuj.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/gnLo7p7.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/XW0I4Ka.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/HQH8oZE.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/G2N0CsJ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/cELdwZK.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/nal1lfz.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Sideshow Collectibles**](https://www.sideshow.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/bvZWW5g.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/LTCQfRB.jpg','新聞','2021-04-12 11:37:11',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',63,7),(561,'《漫威漫畫》「緋紅女巫」1/10比例BDS全身雕像 Iron Studios新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 販售各種流行文化人物的雕像品牌**Iron Studios**，4月10日在[**官網**](https://ironstudios.com/)發布開放預購的 **漫威漫畫》「緋紅女巫」1/10比例BDS全身雕像**官方圖片與訊息，將於2021年第四季發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/RYpg5JX.jpg)\n\n\n##### Iron Studios的新雕像中的猩紅色魔術！\n\n##### 她可以控制混沌魔法，這使她可以操縱概率，甚至扭曲和改變現實，汪達·馬克希莫夫又名“緋紅女巫”，在她能力所及的底座上，在古老的圓柱鐘上，掛著英雄豪宅中的瓦礫，還傳遞著潛意識的訊息，彷彿她在扭曲時空，巫婆用她的雙手操縱一束超自然的紅色能量，而她氣勢磅礡的存在使任何對手都感到恐懼。好像她是直接從漫威的漫畫中走出來，並與她的孿生兄弟短跑選手快銀先前透露的一樣，Iron Studios帶來了她的雕像“《漫威漫畫》「緋紅女巫」1/10比例BDS全身雕像”漫威最強大的神秘女主人公。\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/vRhp4me.jpg)\n\n##### 汪達由傳奇人物史丹·李和傑克·柯比於1964年創立，出生於虛構的Transia –東歐的Wundagore山，與她的兄弟一度被視為萬磁王的女兒，但最近發現兩者都得到了增強被遺傳學家稱為終極進化，最初，她加入了她所謂的“父親”的突變兄弟會，後來與她的兄弟一起由複仇者聯盟在美國隊長的指揮下招募。\n##### 汪達由女星伊麗莎白·奧爾森扮演，並在MCU中進行了改編，但在迪斯尼（Disney +）播出的系列《萬達與幻視》中獲得了更大的知名度和全球知名度，就像在電影和電視劇中一樣，在漫畫中，萬達也和他結婚的合成視線“幻視”發生了戀愛，與該系列不同，在漫畫中，她受到巫師阿加莎·哈克尼斯的指導，成為地球上最強大的魔術操縱者之一。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/0TzkSu8.jpg)\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高13.8吋｜寬7.5吋｜長5.9吋\n##### 預購價格：199.99美元 約5,694新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年第四季\n\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BqeFpEq.jpg)\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/605iTzi.jpg)\n\n##### Scarlet Magic in a new statue from Iron Studios!\n\n##### She can control Chaos Magic, which allows her to manipulate probability and even distort and change reality itself. On a base where she floats with her power, on an old column chime clock, with the remains of rubble from a heroes’ mansion, but also sending a subliminal message as if she were bending time and space, Wanda Maximoff, also known as Scarlet Witch, manipulates bundles of supernatural red energy with her hands, and her imposing presence intimidates any opponent. As if she came straight out of the pages of the Marvel comics, joining forces with her twin brother sprinter Quicksilver previously revealed, Iron Studios brings her statue “Scarlet Witch – X-Men – BDS Art Scale 1/10 – Iron Studios”, with Marvel’s most powerful mystical heroine.\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/J3hlcm7.jpg)\n\n\n##### Created by the legendary Stan Lee and Jack Kirby in 1964, Wanda was born on Wundagore Mountain, in the fictional Transia – Eastern Europe, and, together with her brother, was once considered Magneto’s mutant daughter, but recently it was revealed that both were enhanced by geneticist called High Evolutionary. Initially, she joined the Brotherhood of Mutants of her supposed “father” and later, along with her brother, was recruited by the Avengers under the command of Captain America.\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/uwtMmnB.jpg)\n\n##### Wanda was adapted in the MCU and played by actress Elizabeth Olsen but gained greater prominence and worldwide popularity in the series WandaVision, streamed by Disney+. As in the films and series, in the comics, Wanda also became involved in a romance with the synthezoid Vision, whom he married. Unlike the series, in the comics, she was trained by the witch Agatha Harkness, her mentor, to become one of the most powerful manipulators of magic on Earth.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4xOrDiE.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/YxlEazG.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/oNQ7NHo.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ygsFCiu.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/2Ucapug.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/HWP4KTA.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/rLv3DdI.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/8obtkHr.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Iron Studios**](https://ironstudios.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/e2NZ7i8.png','https://i.imgur.com/RKiX5dW.png','新聞','2021-04-13 04:59:35',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',33,7),(562,'《冰與火之歌：權力遊戲》「Threezero」1/6比例可動人偶 第五季造型 Threezero新品搶先看','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 香港廠牌**Threezero**的願景是使收藏玩具流行起來，給所有人帶來前所未有的歡樂，今日在[**粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/threezeroHK/)宣布即將在4月17日在限定通路進行預訂 **《冰與火之歌：權力遊戲》「Threezero」1/6比例可動人偶**，全球限量1500件。\n\n##### 為慶祝《冰與火之歌：權力遊戲》電視劇集上映10週年，threezero特別推出第5季造形的丹妮莉絲．坦格利安限量版。產品將於4月17日以現貨形式發售，全球限量1,500隻，只限以下網店銷售:\n##### threezero store ︱  https://threezerohk.com\n##### threezero Tmall ︱  https://threezero.tmall.com\n##### Sideshow ︱  https://sideshow.com\n##### BBICN ︱  