riments, Mutagen Man and his ever-changing, mutating form are confined to his mechanical life-support system. But in this incredible glow-in-the-dark colorway exclusive to Entertainment Earth, Super7\'s Ultimates 7-inch action figure is intricately painted in neon shades of pink, yellow, and green! And just like the original version, this Mutagen Man features a massive collection of interchangeable accessories. Take a look at these:\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/obPx8eN.jpg)\n##### 1x Pair of Fist Hands\n##### 1x Pair of Gripping Hands\n##### 1x Mutagen Machine Blaster\n##### 1x Life-Support System\n##### 1x Skull Plug\n##### 1x Fish (Glow)\n##### 1x Wrench (Glow)\n##### 1x Eyeball (Glow)\n##### 1x Turtle (Glow)\n##### 1x Pizza (Glow)\n##### 1x Apple Core (Glow)\n##### 1x Bone (Glow)\n##### 1x Unpainted (Neon Green) Gooey Garbage Rack that holds the Fish, Wrench, Eyeball, Turtle, Pizza, Apple Core, and Bone!\n\n##### The Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Ultimates Glow-in-the-Dark Mutagen Man 7-Inch Action Figure - Entertainment Earth Exclusive comes packaged in deluxe slipcase packaging. Order yours while supplies last!\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/gClzA3J.jpg)\n\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/GPdlgD2.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/A7vDkF5.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/eOfyKnN.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BybAJFd.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/USJPCHz.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Up9IPuQ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/KpkGWTm.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/OKbWHbl.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7S1TN68.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/bQCXocT.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/2aFAAIT.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/xrOsWcv.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/UxlsYU0.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ZnVRMLc.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hlZ4y8H.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/EHWWL2z.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/5QOR6hS.jpg)\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Entertainment Earth**](https://www.entertainmentearth.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/QtTmHGq.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/KEVGjPC.jpg','新聞','2021-04-13 11:56:21',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',47,7),(564,'革命軍巴掌熊《海賊王》「巴索羅繆·大熊」60公分全身雕像 集美殿堂新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 預購總是搶得火熱的日系雕像品牌**集美殿堂**，近日發布開放預購的 **革命軍巴掌熊《海賊王》「巴索羅繆·大熊」60公分全身雕像**官方圖片與訊息，現在可在[**sideshow**](https://www.sideshow.com/collectibles/one-piece-kaido-jimei-palace-908026)官網上預購，將於2021年6月-8月發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BNHLIl5.jpg)\n\n\n##### 巴索羅繆·大熊，也被稱為“暴君”，是王下七武海之一，他是一個非常安靜和鎮定的人，他吃了尼古拉的肉球果實，這使他的手掌上有了腳掌，這些墊子有能力擊退任何東西，它還可以以光速將空氣排斥為手掌狀的衝擊波，並不斷穿透物體，他總是問：“如果你要去旅行，你會去哪裡？”在他利用魔鬼的力量將人們帶到他選擇的地方之前，大熊受到世界政府的高度評價，他是王下七武海中唯一公開宣稱服從世界政府命令的人，但是他一再幫助草帽海盜逃脫了生命，他在恐怖三桅帆船上給許多海盜留下了深刻的印象。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wcoUzZf.jpg)\n##### 集美殿堂製作的巴索羅繆·大熊雕像的場景來自恐怖三桅帆船的戰鬥，雕像中的暴君大熊站在恐怖三桅帆船的廢墟中，釋放出他最強大的技能-爆炸和炸彈。這次襲擊摧毀了所有恐怖三桅帆船，給海盜以強烈的霸氣。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/u5Uipyk.jpg)\n\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高59.9公分｜寬45.9公分｜長37.9.公分\n##### 預購價格：899美元 約25,610新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年6月-8月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hTKfdjw.jpg)\n##### Bartholomew Kuma, also been called ”Tyrant” Kuma, is one of the Seven Warlords of the Sea. He is a very quiet and calm person. He ate the Nikyu Nikyu no Mi a Paramecia-type Devil Fruit that gave him paw pads on the palms of his hands. These pads have the power to repel anything. It can also repel the air into a palm-shaped shock wave at the speed of light and continuously penetrate the object. He always asks \"If you were to go on a trip, where would you go?\" before he uses his devil fruit power to send the people away to where he chooses. Kuma is highly valued by the world government. He is the only person in the Warlord of the Sea who publicly claimed to obey the commands of the World Government, but has repeatedly helped the Straw Hat Pirates escape with their lives. He impressed many pirates in the Thriller bark.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/tPztBqi.jpg)\n##### The scene of the Bartholomew Kuma statue, produced by Jimei Palace, comes from the battle of the Thriller Bark. The tyrant Kuma in the statue stands in the ruins of the Thriller Bark and releases his strongest skills the blast and the bomb. The attack destroyed all the Thriller Bark, giving the pirates a strong sense of domineering.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/162tTbU.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wTAK3qC.jpg)\n##### 圖片來源：[**sideshow**](https://www.sideshow.com/collectibles/one-piece-kaido-jimei-palace-908026)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/Ur9xNLG.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/gC4tHoq.jpg','新聞','2021-04-13 13:02:02',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',60,7),(565,'「悟空-不用擔心。沒有憐憫（NO FEAR. NO MERCY）」1/6比例可動人偶 REBELSIX STUDIO新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### **REBELSIX STUDIO**是經由台灣原型師身上獲得經驗與製作技巧後創立的馬來西亞個人工作室，3月18日發布開放預購的 **「悟空-不用擔心。沒有憐憫（NO FEAR. NO MERCY）」1/6比例可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，可以在[**官網**](https://www.rebelsixstudio.com/)進行預購，將於2021年第二季發售。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/g67iHno.png)\n\n\n##### 全球限量300組\n\n##### 特徵：\n##### ·27個關節！\n##### ·量身定制的詳細服裝與貼花\n##### ·帶有風化細節的風格化設計。\n##### 包括：\n##### ·頭雕悟空\n##### ·12吋關節式素體\n##### ·面具\n##### ·J-Bat\n##### ·3個手榴彈\n##### ·懸浮滑板\n##### ·2對雙手-拳頭，手勢，武器（左，右）\n##### ·1對Rebel Force 1運動鞋（左+右）\n##### ·外套\n##### ·牛仔牛仔褲\n##### ·短袖襯衫\n##### ·1個12吋蛇形支架底座組\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubborn