ce-908026)官網上預購，將於2021年11月-2022年1月發售。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/x5XBDhg.png)\n\n##### 黑暗女主人身著9吋高的全手工製作的雕像，穿著所有原始的、獨特的、優雅的、蝙蝠風格的哥特式禮服，她完美的吸引著目光，艾維拉的長衫以垂墜的領口和垂褶的袖子為主題，以黑色、灰色、紫色的黃昏和暮色的夜空為主題，將她曲線優美的每一吋都帶入了立體生活，在裙擺和袖子上重複出現一種新穎的蝙蝠和漩渦狀圖案，並刻入了禮服的造型中，其他裝飾包括在她的黑色鞋子上飾有金色凸起的蜘蛛圖案以及珠光耳環，仿製的，值得貴族使用的閃閃發光的紅寶石裝飾著艾維拉的腰帶，戒指和耳環上的標誌性匕首，整個合唱團以流行文化偶像的經典服裝呈現出全新的時裝風格。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/atkExBc.jpg)\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/pLoXI9S.jpg)\n\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高9吋\n##### 預購價格：80美元 約2,276新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年11月-2022年1月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/LI3QL2Z.jpg)\n##### The Mistress of the Dark dons a runway-ready all original eerily elegant bat-inspired goth gown befitting her undeniably seductive appeal in this all handcrafted figure standing 9” tall. Themed in dusk and twilight night sky color tones of blacks, greys and purples, Elvira’s slit gown with plunging neckline and draped sleeves brings every inch of her curvy splendor to three-dimensional life. A novel bat and swirl pattern incised into the sculpt of the dress repeats across the skirt and sleeves. Other embellishments include a golden raised spider design atop her black shoes as well as pearlescent earrings. Faux faceted gleaming rubies worthy of royalty adorn Elvira’s iconic dagger on her belt, ring and earrings. The whole ensemble presents an all-new Couture take on the pop culture icon’s classic costume. Make this sensational new figure part of your collection!\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/brfCl5F.jpg)\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/valGinp.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hxcNMkc.jpg)\n##### 圖片來源：[**sideshow**](https://www.sideshow.com/collectibles/one-piece-kaido-jimei-palace-908026)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/ixKy126.png','','新聞','2021-04-14 06:38:41',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',34,7),(567,'邪惡使者《決勝時空戰區》「骷髏王」1/6比例可動人偶 Mondo新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 美國藝術品牌**Mondo**剛開始是在電影院地下儲藏室販賣衣服的商店，後來與藝術家合作販售海報、唱片，才有如今的品牌發展，昨日發布開放預購的 **《決勝時空戰區》「骷髏王」1/6比例可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，可以在[**官網**](https://mondoshop.com/collections/all/products/adventure-time-statue-jake-and-finn-regular-version#featured-video)進行預購，將於2021年4月發售。\n\n##### 《決勝時空戰區》「骷髏王」1/6比例可動人偶高12吋，附上凱多王子的頭雕與骷髏王的頭雕，還有兩把槍及兩把劍、替換手等，預購價格為185美元。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/MDAaepL.jpg)\n\n\n##### 在成為骷髏王之前很久，他就被稱為凱多王子，曾經是高貴的皇室成員，蘭道爾國王的兄弟和叔叔... 亞當！凱多王子生氣，因為未來的惡棍很容易產生，因此打開了他的兄弟，對智慧殿堂發動了進攻，凱多王子失敗了，最終被蘭多國王擊敗，失敗了，並因失敗的攻擊而受了重傷，凱多王子再次試圖通過向他的兄弟投擲酸來傷害他的兄弟。不幸的是，這適得其反，是凱多王子被毀容了。\n##### 為了拯救自己的生命，凱多王子迫切希望自己的導師霍達克拯救他，在此過程中，霍達克將凱多王子轉變為被稱為骷髏王的反派！\n##### 這個凱多王子人物既展示了他的原始外觀，又展示了他向骷髏王的轉變。擁有他的兩個著名的刀片，衝擊波，中間變形的頭骨，傷害他的酸惡行為，最後是Alcala骷髏王的頭部，這個收藏品為每個人提供了一個舞台，並且是炫耀凱多王子以前所有榮耀的最可怕的方式！\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NPayRqU.jpg)\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ZwnPbba.gif)\n\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高12吋\n##### 預購價格：185美元 約5,264新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年4月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/rGLS481.jpg)\n##### Long before he became Skeletor, he was known as Keldor. Once high royalty, the brother of King Randor and uncle to Prince...ADAM! Keldor being angry as future villains are prone to do turned on a his brother and staged an attack on the Hall of Wisdom. Keldor is unsuccessful, and ultimately defeated by King Randor. Having failed, and becoming severely injured from the failed attack, Keldor tries once more to hurt his brother by throwing a vile of acid at him. This, sadly, backfires, and it is Keldor who is disfigured.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SA4hpmr.jpg)\n##### Desperate to save his own life, Keldor turns to his mentor Hordak to save him. And in the process, Hordak transforms Keldor into the villain known as Skeletor!\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/bwXJPVd.jpg)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/yIeqaho.jpg)\n##### This Keldor Figure showcases both his original appearance and his transformation into Skeletor. Featuring his two famous blades, blasters, a mid-transformation skull, the acid vile that wounded him, and finally, the Alcala Skeletor head. This collectible has a stage for everybody, and is the gruesomely best way to show off Keldor in all his former glory!\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/h8C7KoK.jpg)\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/2bFZDG9.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3QGVpIk.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/eLE9PBy.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/LBj1Mb9.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/YucnMI2.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/eNufoEx.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/O2Toqy5.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hZS4FFr.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Svb3TNS.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/lnNJtht.jpg)\n##### 圖片來源：[**Mondo**](https://mondoshop.com/collections/all/products/adventure-time-statue-jake-and-finn-regular-version#featured-video)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/f94i30G.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/EpsLQar.png','新聞','2021-04-14 10:29:39',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',44,7),(568,'《ECW》「仙人掌傑克 WWE Elite」Ringside獨家版7吋可動人偶 Mattel新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 世界摔角娛樂《WWE》可動人偶系列目前由知名大廠**Mattel（美泰兒）** 公司製造，近日發布開放預購的 **《ECW》「仙人掌傑克 WWE Elite」Ringside獨家版7吋可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，可以在第一大《WWE》經銷商[**Ringside Collectibles**](https://www.ringsidecollectibles.com/)進行預購，將於2021年八月下旬發售。\n\n##### 仙人掌傑克本名米克·佛利（Mick Foley），還有其他稱號，像是瘋狂的類人克（Mankind）以及Dude Love，曾經拿下過3次WWE冠軍、8次WWE雙打冠軍、2次ECW雙打冠軍及1次WCW雙打冠軍，並入選入選2013年世界摔角娛樂名人堂，令人驚訝的是佛利同時是位作家，此產品高約7吋，附上冠軍腰帶、替換手，預購價格為27.99美元。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://www.ringsidecollectibles.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/22/wm37_mattel_001.jpg)\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高7吋\n##### 預購價格：27.99美元 約796新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年八月下旬\n\n\n![](https://www.ringsidecollectibles.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/22/rex_182_ecw_cactus_jack_instagram.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Ringside Collectibles**](https://www.ringsidecollectibles.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/4CQ1jJ1.png','https://i.imgur.com/PKOTdYu.png','新聞','2021-04-14 10:56:36',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',32,7),(569,'《金剛戰士》「大獸神＆豬怪（Pudgy Pig）＆綠戰士＆紅戰士＆魔土鬼面卒＆幽冥女王」3.75吋可動人偶 SUPER7新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 專製3.75吋及7吋可動人偶的美國廠牌**SUPER7**，4月10日在[**官網**](https://super7.com/?fbclid=IwAR2Ha_LUnCX7_H0MfBtgCQZI6Dq_tLlpIWri2oYb_UpDSkqEv8yayHkLZOw)發布開放預購的 **《金剛戰士》「大獸神＆豬怪（Pudgy Pig）＆綠戰士＆紅戰士＆魔土鬼面卒＆幽冥女王」3.75吋可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，將於2021年4月發售。\n\n##### 是嗎啡時間！我們將以一對態度堅定的少年，一個超大型的獸神，一個邪惡的女皇以及她的幾個僕人來開始我們的“強大的金剛戰士”人物系列。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/9xDglUG.jpg)\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高大獸神高6吋 其他高3.75吋\n##### 預購價格：大獸神24美元 約682新台幣 其他單款18美元 約512新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年4月\n\n##### **大獸神**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3xeI6Rv.jpg)\n##### 結合在一起的五隻恐龍的力量不可阻擋！這款超大型大獸神可動人物身高6吋，並配有劍和盾牌配件，使用這個大獸神可動人物，讓Angel Grove和您的金剛戰士系列免受幽冥女王的眾多怪物侵擾！\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/bw0G1nJ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/o06pY2F.png)\n\n##### **豬怪（Pudgy Pig）**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/xnCbf0l.jpg)\n##### 單單是豬怪的無盡食慾就足以與金剛戰隊相提並論！這款關節式，超大號的可動人物配有巨大的刀叉配件，千萬不要錯過獲得魚匠人和幽冥女王最令人難忘的怪物之一-隨手準備一些辛辣食物，以防萬一這個可動人物試圖吞噬整個金剛戰士系列！ \n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qoKJnkM.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### **綠戰士**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/t4zJAV3.jpg)\n##### 綠戰士在幽冥女王的影響下還是忠於金剛戰士？有了這個3.75吋關節式可動人物，您就可以決定！綠戰士帶有他的龍匕首和黑暗之劍配件。現在，您有史以來最偉大的強大的金剛戰士之一！\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/pXup18i.jpg)\n\n\n##### **紅戰士**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/5cIaOpd.jpg)\n##### 強大的金剛戰隊的負責人和霸王龍Rein Dinozord的駕駛員，那就是紅戰士！此3.75吋關節式可動人物配有Power Sword和兩個Blade Blasters配件，沒有比啟動紅戰士更好的地方來開始您的強大的金剛戰士可動系列！\n![](https://i.imgur.com/5Cc6TL8.jpg)\n\n##### **魔土鬼面卒**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/fRB0LCf.jpg)\n##### 每個壞蛋都需要一群步兵來戰鬥，而魔土鬼面卒正是幽冥女王的服從者！這款3.75吋關節式可動魔土鬼面卒人物帶有可互換的鏟刀和巨石臂，組建一支由自己的膩子巡邏隊可動人物組成的軍隊，以使您的強大金剛戰士忙碌，而魚匠人和幽冥女王會為他們拼殺一個怪物！\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Uc8Xf4j.png)\n\n##### **幽冥女王**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/MfUjmVW.jpg)\n##### 並不是每天都可以將這個邪惡的皇后握在手中，但是有了幽冥女王可動人物，您將獲得難得的機會！這款強大的金剛戰士幽冥女王3.75吋關節式可動人物帶有她的魔杖配件，幽冥女王擁有高級裝飾，是任何強大的金剛戰士迷的必備裝備！\n![](https://i.imgur.com/8Rtb3ow.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**SUPER7**](https://preorder.super7store.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/bFCG5n8.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/jYdpPqp.jpg','新聞','2021-04-14 11:49:43',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',17,7),(570,'《變形金剛》「羅迪至尊」1/10比例全身雕像 XM Studios新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 新加坡雕像廠商**XM Studios**擁有多種角色產品線，並想證明小規模團隊也能做出高品質產品，昨日發布旗下**1:10 Scale Transformers Premium Collectibles系列**的 **《變形金剛》「羅迪至尊」1/10比例全身雕像**官方圖片與訊息，並在格林威治標準時間4月14日下午六點開放預購，可以在[**官網**](https://www.xm-studios.com/pages/default.aspx)進行預購。\n\n##### 羅迪是位血氣方剛的少年，會受到母體的影響變成羅迪至尊，高92公分，配件附上2個替換右手：握槍、握長步槍，2個替換左手：握槍、握原能矩陣，旁邊還有載具型態的藍寶堅尼，藍寶堅尼與全身各處都具有照明功能，預購價格為1,979.1新加坡幣，限量499件。\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qGB3vH8.jpg)\n\n\n##### XM Studios很高興展示我們的下一個1:10 Scale Transformers Premium Collectibles系列羅迪至尊！每個手工製作的雕像都經過手工上漆，並具有高品質的裝飾，瘋狂地熱愛著變形金剛G1卡通時代的團隊，從零開始精心製作的每一顆螺母，螺栓和電線都經過精心設計和雕刻，受童年時代最喜歡的80年代卡通之一的啟發，我們採用了G1的標誌性外形設計，並通過XM對它們進行了現代細節處理，以更好地適應當今對複雜機器人設計的期望，我們不遺餘力地設計了這些原創作品，使我們的核心團隊花了將近兩年的時間，實現了復古美感與時尚現代細節的驚人平衡。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/K07ChTF.jpg)\n\n##### Rodimus Prime Premium Collectibles雕像特徵：\n\n##### 受《變形金剛：電影》的啟發，Rodimus Prime準備戰鬥！\n##### ●尤尼克隆主題底座\n##### ●2右手：1把槍，1把長步槍\n##### ●2個左手：1個握槍，1個握著原能矩陣\n##### ●載具型態：汽車\n##### ●具照亮功能的眼睛\n##### ●由冷鑄瓷製成\n##### ●ES：MTO（最高499）\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hFhasFC.jpg)\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高92公分｜寬32公分｜長52公分\n##### 預購價格：1,979.1新加坡幣 約42,015新台幣\n##### 發售日期：未公布\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/HbwcCYm.jpg)\n##### XM Studios is excited to present our next 1:10 Scale Transformers Premium Collectibles series statue, Rodimus Prime! Each handcrafted statue is individually hand-painted with the quality finish. Crafted from scratch, every nut, bolt and wire is lovingly designed and sculpted ground up by a team in mad love with the Transformers G1 era of cartoons. Inspired by one of our childhood favourite 80s cartoon, we took the G1\'s iconic form design and XM-ized them with modern details, to better fit in today\'s expectations of sophisticated robotry designs. We have spared no effort and designing these original pieces took our core team almost 2 years, resulting in an amazing balance of retro beauty with a sleek modern details.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/GGg3dxo.jpg)\n \n\n##### Rodimus Prime Premium Collectibles statue features:\n\n##### Inspired by The Transformers: The Movie, Rodimus Prime readies for battle!\n##### Unicron theme inspired base\n##### 2 Right hands: 1 holding gun, 1 holding long rifle\n##### 2 Left hands: 1 holding gun, 1 holding the Matrix of leadership\n##### Alternate Vehicle Mode: Car\n##### Light up eyes\n##### Crafted from cold-cast porcelain\n##### ES: MTO (Max 499)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/bEPs7kX.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7H9bqzB.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/UQWBRU2.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/prO58Ny.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/gjhmoEc.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qeXlTWN.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/uh3cXM6.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mcPOzlA.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hTDTq6g.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/QrQbfxJ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/sZIunOO.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/XwVd5dk.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/HXSORqj.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/WeDuX5H.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/UdwQ0Y6.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/bUXHjXk.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/65aQ60G.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/At7pSRB.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6DpRpkL.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4qvSDdd.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/CH3PhLw.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/cAAALWe.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/44OnPNX.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VEntPXz.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4FBge0G.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/rPQi9hq.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1Ntq4M4.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Dr7PbBe.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/uG3HVus.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qICxZBX.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**XM Studios**](https://www.xm-studios.com/pages/default.aspx)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/cEbOPqX.png','https://i.imgur.com/s5U1q4O.png','新聞','2021-04-15 04:58:17',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',26,7),(571,'《烙印勇士》「凱茲對戰左德」普通/豪華版 1/6比例收藏雕像 Prime 1 Studio新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 日本雕像品牌**Prime 1 Studio**專製時下最具話題的熱門人物雕像，昨日發布旗下**Ultimate Diorama Masterline系列**的 **《烙印勇士》「凱茲對戰左德」普通/豪華版 1/6比例收藏雕像**官方圖片與訊息，並宣布日本時間4月15日下午3:00開放預購，可以在[**官網**](https://www.prime1studio.com/)進行預購，將於2022年7月-10月發售。\n\n##### 《烙印勇士》「凱茲對戰左德」普通/豪華版 1/6比例收藏雕像高50.9公分，附上替換頭雕，豪華版多附上兩個替換頭雕，背後披風可拆卸與可彎曲，普通版預購價格為999美元，豪華版1,099美元。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/nCwYjxr.jpg)\n##### “如果我眨眼，他會睜開我的頭！” – Guts\n\n##### Prime 1 Studio再次自豪地向您展示Ultimate Diorama Masterline系列的最新功能：令人難以置信的《烙印勇士》「凱茲對戰左德」普通/豪華版 1/6比例收藏雕像！\n\n##### 盡我們最大的努力來紀念傳奇的Berserk創作者Miura Kentarou Miura，Prime 1 Studio忠實地重現了野獸劍客與黑劍客之間的史詩般的衝突……及時凍結了！\n\n##### 凱茲激怒了左德應該敢站在他和他的quarry古力菲斯之間，並用左德鎖定了劍！左德宣稱膽量必須經過他才能獲得古力菲斯！但是這次會面不像凱茲上次與左德發生衝突！\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/8zcM5qh.jpg)\n##### Prime 1 Studio在雄偉的20吋立體模型環境中註入了動感的動作，這些戰略性和嫻熟的戰鬥人員在白雪皚皚的景觀中留下了雷鳴般的印象，周圍環繞著里基特精心製作的斬龍劍，我們的靈巧的雕塑家給左德注入了怪異的體態，冷酷的面容和險惡的姿態，我們雕刻了膽量，以熟練地阻止左德的進攻，這說明了凱茲的斬龍劍開始破解左德的劍的那一刻，我們為左德配備了人造皮草纏腰布，對於凱茲，他的盔甲中的每個細節，凹痕和叮叮聲都得到了忠實的再現，我們的畫家將這個立體模型盡可能地貼近了三浦健太郎對這場史詩般的戰鬥的想像。\n\n##### 對於豪華版，通過在凱茲的三個替換頭雕之一間切換來增加戲劇性！或通過附加他的英勇可擺姿勢的織物斗篷來提升凱茲的傳奇才能！\n\n\n##### 規格：\n##### 狂暴主題底座\n##### 3個替換凱茲頭（三種不同的表達方式）【豪華版】\n##### 1個可拆卸可彎曲織物披風\n![](https://i.imgur.com/UXV1tlU.jpg)\n\n\n##### \n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/YTYt5tR.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高50.9公分｜寬65.6公分｜長34.5公分\n##### 預購價格：普通版999美元 約28,319新台幣\n##### 豪華版1,099美元 約31,154新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2022年7月-10月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ppYd2RW.jpg)\n\n##### \"If I blink, he’ll split my head open!” – Guts\n\n##### Prime 1 Studio is, once again, proud to present the latest addition to the Ultimate Diorama Masterline Series: The incredible 1/6 Scale Guts Versus Zodd from Berserk!\n\n##### Doing our best to honor legendary Berserk creator, Kentarou Miura, Prime 1 Studio has faithfully recreated an epic clash between the Beast Swordsman and the Black Swordsman…frozen in time!\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/QI8aXvz.jpg)\n##### Guts, enraged that Zodd should dare stand between him and his quarry Griffith, has locked swords with Zodd! Zodd exclaims that Guts must go through him to get to Griffith! But this meeting is not like the last time Guts clashed with Zodd. Two years of Apostle-hunting has increased Guts’ power level so much, that even he is surprised that he can go toe-to-toe with the demon Apostle Zodd!\n\n##### Prime 1 Studio has imbued this majestic 20-inch diorama environment with dynamic action as these strategic and skillful combatants make their thundering impressions in the snowy landscape, surrounded by tribute swords lovingly crafted by Rickert. Our deft sculptors have imbued Zodd with a monstrous physique, a grim visage, and a menacing stance. We have sculpted Guts to hold back Zodd’s attack with skillful ease, illustrating the very moment Guts’ Dragonslayer has started to crack Zodd’s sword. We have equipped Zodd with a synthetic fur loincloth, and for Guts, every detail, dent, and ding in his armor is faithfully recreated. Our painters have rendered this diorama as closely as we can to Kentarou Miura’s vision of this epic battle.\n\n##### And for the Deluxe Version, add to the drama by switching between one of three interchangeable expressions for Guts! Or level-up Guts’ legendary prowess by attaching his heroic poseable fabric cape!\n\n\n##### Specifications:\n##### Berserk themed base\n##### Three (3) Interchangeable Guts Heads (Three different expressions)\n##### One (1) Detachable Poseable Guts Fabric Cape\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1RkmHnJ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/9TGH03I.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/C8rBQmO.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/q1tm1RC.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/yNA4BOw.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/kAjEHog.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1dS5deZ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/RkZTOdS.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/uhlnk60.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/lYknW5V.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/T9Tmdd3.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/8jbagTf.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6TAhqz8.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/PQVmhgK.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/l8KYeRn.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qipObdE.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/vNQYEQH.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/jkPEN7R.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/UQEA53k.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Nc7Fhwu.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Wu2Sj9j.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VajnKmh.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Dir8Y6N.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/FZru9T6.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/iUus0Og.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hVkGe0A.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qGreL2g.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hWFQakm.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/YVeGrNm.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Prime 1 Studio**](https://www.prime1studio.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/IXLmw3B.png','https://i.imgur.com/TXQFRdQ.jpg','新聞','2021-04-15 09:09:20',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',34,7),(572,'第一波《銀河飛龍》「畢凱艦長＆百科＆解難＆衛斯理·克拉夏＆武夫＆博格」3.75吋可動人偶 SUPER7新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 專製3.75吋及7吋可動人偶的美國廠牌**SUPER7**，昨日發布《銀河飛龍》系列第一波 **「畢凱艦長＆百科＆解難＆衛斯理·克拉夏＆武夫＆博格」3.75吋可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，現在可以在[**官網**](https://super7.com/?fbclid=IwAR2Ha_LUnCX7_H0MfBtgCQZI6Dq_tLlpIWri2oYb_UpDSkqEv8yayHkLZOw)進行預購，將於2021年7月發售。\n\n\n##### 您不需要正子腦就能弄清楚第一波《銀河飛龍》可動人物有多棒！畢凱艦長，百科，解難，衛斯理·克拉夏，武夫，博格都在這裡！\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/sRmgyjo.jpg)\n\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高3.75吋\n##### 預購價格：單款18美元 約509新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年7月\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ZBpY9Ib.jpg)\n\n##### **畢凱艦長**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/kLSqLtE.jpg)\n##### 星際飛船企業號隊長尚路克·畢凱，他是一位勇敢的探險家和哲學外交家，他是所有季的經典人物。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/MUUdL8Y.jpg)\n\n##### **百科**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qgx2MQR.jpg)\n##### Noonien Soong博士不在Super7陣容中，但看到此人物後，您可能會這麼想！\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Xprc5no.jpg)\n\n\n##### **解難**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/90MFyh7.jpg)\n##### 如果沒有解難提出明智的建議和永恆的智慧，Forward將只是另一艘星際船上的另一個休息室，而不是傳說中的企業號心臟。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/036G9XP.jpg)\n\n##### **衛斯理·克拉夏**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/A9Lxp2V.jpg)\n##### 星際艦隊歷史上沒有哪個少尉比衛斯理·克拉夏挽救了更多生命或挫敗了更多災難。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Q6i7PUl.jpg)\n\n##### **武夫**\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3MVIKyT.jpg)\n##### “我是克林貢人！如果您對此表示懷疑，可以安排一次遊行！” 不管是否有星際艦隊軍官，毫無疑問，沃爾夫中尉是真正的克林貢戰士。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/EW1b6ve.jpg)\n\n##### **博格**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VQzkFwi.jpg)\n##### 如果您不希望其他人被博格族人吸收，最好將博格放在包裝中。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ZKhrWZY.jpg)\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**SUPER7**](https://preorder.super7store.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/tFHs9iD.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/YJuPHkK.jpg','新聞','2021-04-15 10:07:23',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',32,7),(573,'探長＆法國警察《粉紅豹》「彼得·塞勒斯」豪華版1/6比例可動人偶 Infinite Statue新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 義大利廠牌**Infinite Statue**的誕生是為了那些想要獨特且不可複制的苛刻收藏家創造物品，4月9日發布開放預購的 **《粉紅豹》「彼得·塞勒斯」豪華版1/6比例可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，現在可以在[**官網**](https://www.infinitestatue.com/it/)進行預購，將於2021年第三季發售。\n\n##### 《粉紅豹》「彼得·塞勒斯」豪華版1/6比例可動人偶高29公分，以PVC作為材料製作，配件附上兩個頭雕、探長服裝、法國警察服裝、替換頭髮與帽子、武器等配件，豪華版預購價格為379.99歐元，兩種版本的成套服裝與素體可以個別購買，預購價格為單款275歐元。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/aiasoro.jpg)\n\n\n\n\n##### Infinite Statue和高斯提·普拉斯蒂克（Kaustic Plastik）開創了豪華版可動人物：彼得·塞勒斯，這是我們專門針對可動人物的新系列，彼得·塞勒斯1/6比例是在法國著名的《粉紅豹》中的角色，上面有布衣服和豐富的配件。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/S5rVlLF.jpg)\n##### 彼得·塞勒斯是喜劇和轉型的天才，是一位出色的英國演員，風格鮮明，為我們帶來了有史以來最有趣的插科打，作為布雷克·愛德華茲導演的電影系列中笨拙的探長雅克·克洛索，令人難忘的是，彼得·塞勒斯現在將在一系列新的可動人偶中扮演Infinite Statue和高斯提·普拉斯蒂克（Kaustic Plastik）的豪華版人物。\n\n##### 彼得·塞勒斯的每個版本都可以1/6比例定製，並經過精心的照顧和關注，賦予人物真實感和相似性，從他喜劇的眼睛表情，衣服的質地到對象和物體，配件，這是法國著名探長的明確組成部分。\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/PYe8zna.jpg)\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高29公分\n##### 預購價格：349.99歐元 約11,861新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年第三季\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/kk4VzlQ.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/c1v5bK5.jpg)\n##### Infinite Statue e Kaustic Plastik presentano: Peter Sellers L’Inspecteur edition che inaugura “Action! Deluxe Figure”, la nostra nuova linea dedicata alle action figures. Peter Sellers nei panni del famoso Ispettore francese è in scala 1/6, con vestiti in stoffa e una ricca serie di accessori.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hemv8lX.jpg)\n\n##### Genio assoluto di comicità e trasformismo, Peter Sellers è il grande attore inglese dallo stile inconfondibile che ci ha regalato gags tra le più divertenti di tutti i tempi. Indimenticabile nei panni del maldestro Inspecteur Jacques Clouseau nella serie di film del regista Blake Edwards, Peter Sellers è ora protagonista per Infinite Statue e Kaustic Plastik di una nuova serie di action figure che inaugurano la linea Action! Deluxe Figure.\n\n##### Ogni versione di Peter Sellers è in scala 1/6 posizionabile, ed è stata realizzata con meticolosa cura e attenzione per dare alla figura realismo e somiglianza, a partire dalla sua comica espressione degli occhi, la trama dei vestiti, fino agli oggetti e accessori, che sono parte inconfondibile del famoso ispettore francese.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mKxYIwr.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/urzWgvw.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/r07jr0O.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/G2aU5sO.jpg)\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Infinite Statue**](https://www.infinitestatue.com/it/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/oEONV9x.png','https://i.imgur.com/ENu2XBv.png','新聞','2021-04-15 11:06:17',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',46,7),(574,'世界瀕臨毀滅《怪獸總進擊》「Round 2盒組」Mezco Toyz新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n\n##### 擅長製造恐怖角色的美式品牌**Mezco Toyz**，今日發布**旗下5 Points XL廠牌**開放預購的 **《怪獸總進擊》「Round 2盒組」Mezco Toyz新品**官方圖片與訊息，可以在[**官網**](https://www.mezcotoyz.com/)進行預購，將於2021年11月-2022年1月發售。\n\n##### 《怪獸總進擊》「Round 2盒組」包含：王者基多拉、迷你拉、哥羅龍、巴拉剛，配件為2個巴拉剛替換頭雕、1對巴拉剛替換腿、3個王者基多拉重力光束特效、2個迷你拉頭雕、2對迷你拉武器、1個迷你拉原子呼吸特效、4個展示底座，預購價格為85美元\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wGbh9Eg.jpg)\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/9XXcsS9.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 5 Points XL-在我們懷舊的5 Points系列產品中增加了巨大的內容，具有相同的以風扇為動力的樂趣，但更大！…這有點大事了。 \n\n##### 隨著外太空與三個怪獸的國王爭奪戰繼續進行，這是一場巨大的全面進攻！\n\n##### 《怪獸總進擊》「Round 2盒組」包含王者基多拉、迷你拉、哥羅龍、巴拉剛，還包括可替換的頭雕、手臂、腿部、特效。\n\n \n\n##### 世界瀕臨毀滅《怪獸總進擊》「Round 2盒組」包括：\n##### 王者基多拉 –這只三頭太空龍也是哥吉拉的頭號敵人！王者基多拉帶有三個重力光束特效，可以連接到他的三個頭上。\n##### 迷你拉 –哥吉拉的兒子，迷你拉配備了替換手臂，替換頭雕和附在頭上的原子呼吸特效……他仍在鍛煉整個原子呼吸。 \n##### 哥羅龍 –巨型恐龍，它利用跳躍踢來攻擊，類似於袋鼠。 \n##### 巴拉剛 -一種四足的，有角的恐龍狀生物，眾所周知，巴拉剛會跳遠距離，深入地底，然後用他的頭鑽出，巴拉剛帶有替換頭雕和替換雙腿。\n \n\n##### 配件：\n##### 2個巴拉剛替換頭雕\n##### 1對巴拉剛替換腿\n##### 3個王者基多拉重力光束特效\n##### 2個迷你拉頭雕\n##### 2對迷你拉武器\n##### 1個迷你拉原子呼吸特效\n##### 4個展示底座\n \n\n##### 5 Points XL《怪獸總進擊》「Round 2盒組」包裝在易於收藏的盒子中，專為收藏家而設計。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/OONYeNF.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：未公布\n##### 預購價格：85美元 約2,408新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年11月-2022年1月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/dK2XbU2.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/J8jZfQc.jpg)\n##### 5 Points XL - a colossal addition to our nostalgic 5 Points line with the same fan-fueled fun, but bigger!  …It’s a little bit of a big deal. \n\n##### It’s an all-out attack of monstrous proportions as the battle against the three-headed kaiju king from outer space continues!\n\n##### This second bursting box of behemoths contains King Ghidorah, Manilla, Gorosaurus, and Baragon and includes select interchangeable heads, arms, legs, or FX.\n\n \n![](https://i.imgur.com/BK718NJ.jpg)\n\n##### THE 5 POINTS XL DESTROY ALL MONSTERS (1968): ROUND 2 SET INCLUDES:\n##### King Ghidorah – This three-headed space dragon is also Godzilla’s arch-enemy! King Ghidorah comes with three gravity beam FX that can attach to his three head portraits.\n##### Minilla – son of Godzilla. Minilla comes with alternate arms, an alternate head portrait, and his signature atomic smoke ring FX that attaches to his head portrait... he’s still working out the whole atomic breath thing. \n##### Gorosaurus – The giant dinosaur that utilizes a leaping kick attack, similar to that of a kangaroo. \n##### Baragon – A four-legged, horned dinosaur-like creature. Baragon is known to leap long distances, burrow deep into the ground, and use his head to get his point across. Baragon comes with an alternate head portrait and an alternate pair of legs.\n \n\n##### ACCESSORIES:\n##### Two (2) Baragon head portraits\n##### One (1) pair of Baragon legs\n##### Three (3) King Ghidorah gravity beam FX\n##### Two (2) Minilla head portraits\n##### Two (2) pairs of Minilla arms\n##### One (1) Miniilla atomic smoke ring FX\n##### Four (4) display bases\n \n\n##### 5 Points XL Destroy All Monsters (1968): Round 2 is packaged in a collector-friendly box, designed with collectors in mind.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/A1bfkLG.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BSMNiug.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BUYFXTk.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Q0dyGZD.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/C0FXOrb.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/dE5AeQt.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3m2syNr.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ziTP3FW.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6xUXcok.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hh6OABa.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BsBEgi5.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/UuX9VPU.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/0zomnGj.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/fCn3gr7.jpg)\n##### 圖片來源：[**Mezco Toyz**](https://www.mezcotoyz.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/Dm2Tomv.png','','新聞','2021-04-16 06:05:00',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',14,7),(575,'世界瀕臨毀滅《怪獸總進擊》「Round 1盒組」Mezco Toyz新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 擅長製造恐怖角色的美式品牌**Mezco Toyz**，今日發布**旗下5 Points XL廠牌**開放預購的 **《怪獸總進擊》「Round 1盒組」Mezco Toyz新品**官方圖片與訊息，可以在[**官網**](https://www.mezcotoyz.com/)進行預購，將於2021年11月-2022年1月發售。\n\n##### 《怪獸總進擊》「Round 1盒組」包含：哥吉拉、莫斯拉，安基拉斯和拉頓、2對哥吉拉武器、2對哥吉拉替換手、1個哥吉拉原子呼吸特效、1個莫斯拉網狀絲的特效、2個安基拉斯替換頭雕、2個拉頓頭雕、2個展示底座，預購價格為85美元。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/f6rPKUP.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/W1Qzkmx.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 5 Points XL-在我們懷舊的5 Points系列產品中增加了巨大的內容，具有相同的以風扇為動力的樂趣，但更大！…這有點大事了。 \n\n##### 怪物們起義了……世界瀕臨毀滅！\n\n##### 受到1968年電影的啟發，這種巨大的kaiju箱子幾乎無法容納怪物樂園的野獸-哥吉拉、莫斯拉，安基拉斯和拉頓！\n\n \n![](https://i.imgur.com/TpvrpOe.jpg)\n\n##### 5 Points XL《怪獸總進擊》「Round 1盒組」包括：\n##### 哥吉拉 –怪物之王！哥吉拉配有一對替換手臂，一個替換頭雕，以及他的簽名原子呼吸特效（附著在他的一張頭雕上）。 \n##### 莫斯拉 –幼蟲期描繪了巨大的飛蛾女神，莫斯拉帶有附在她嘴上網狀絲的特效。\n##### 安基拉斯 –敵還是友？這款五人式的挖土Kaiju帶有替換的閉口頭雕。\n##### 拉頓 –輻照的翼龍和飛行威脅！拉頓有一個替換的閉口頭雕。\n \n\n##### 配件：\n##### 2對哥吉拉武器\n##### 2對哥吉拉替換手\n##### 1個哥吉拉原子呼吸特效\n##### 1個莫斯拉網狀絲的特效。\n##### 2個安基拉斯替換頭雕\n##### 2個拉頓頭雕\n##### 2個展示底座\n \n\n##### 5 Points XL《怪獸總進擊》「Round 1盒組」包裝在易於收藏的盒子中，專為收藏家而設計。\n\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1kpE4Ug.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/beKtEzG.jpg)\n\n##### 尺寸：未公布\n##### 預購價格：85美元 約2,408新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年11月-2022年1月\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/HyZBs4q.jpg)\n\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 5 Points XL - a colossal addition to our nostalgic 5 Points line with the same fan-fueled fun, but bigger!  …It’s a little bit of a big deal. \n\n##### The monsters are in revolt…and the world is on the brink of destruction!\n\n##### Inspired by the 1968 film, this colossal crate of kaiju can barely contain the beasts of Monsterland - Godzilla, Mothra, Anguirus, and Rodan!\n\n \n![](https://i.imgur.com/2912dNv.jpg)\n\n##### THE 5 POINTS XL GODZILLA: DESTROY ALL MONSTERS (1968): ROUND 1 BOXED SET INCLUDES:\n##### Godzilla – King of the Monsters! Godzilla comes with a pair of alternate arms, an alternate head portrait, and his signature atomic breath FX that attaches to one of his head portraits. \n##### Mothra – The giant moth goddess is depicted in her larval stage. Mothra comes with a web FX that attaches to her mouth.\n##### Anguirus – Friend or foe? This five-brained burrowing Kaiju comes with an alternate closed-mouth head portrait.\n##### Rodan – Irradiated Pteranodon and flying menace! Rodan comes with an alternate closed-mouth head portrait.\n \n\n##### ACCESSORIES:\n##### Two (2) pairs of Godzilla arms\n##### Two (2) Godzilla head portraits\n##### One (1) Godzilla atomic breath FX\n##### One (1) Mothra web FX\n##### Two (2) Anguirus head portraits\n##### Two (2) Rodan head portraits\n##### Two (2) display bases\n \n\n##### 5 Points XL Godzilla: Destroy All Monsters (1968): Round 1 Boxed Set is packaged in a collector-friendly box, designed with collectors in mind.\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/e1jlCnX.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/puxy9kb.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3GQoyVs.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NqAl6AH.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/huE6uH8.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Y6UyepK.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/iqQwD6G.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4Lv7mR0.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/c1WeFAL.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mMkxZpo.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/LD6zBmo.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/RlihDFq.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/nxeknKe.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/JmCkshI.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Mezco Toyz**](https://www.mezcotoyz.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n\n','https://i.imgur.com/cWb3okG.png','','新聞','2021-04-16 06:05:59',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',36,7),(576,'《黑暗之夜：死亡金屬》「狂笑蝙蝠 蘇打罐包裝」4.25吋靜態完成品 Funko新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 美國超Q大頭娃娃品牌**Funko**，昨日發布開放預購的 **《黑暗之夜：死亡金屬》「狂笑蝙蝠 蘇打罐包裝」4.25吋靜態完成品**官方圖片與訊息，可以在[**previewsworld**](https://www.previewsworld.com/Catalog/AUG208757)進行預購，將於2021年6月30日發售。\n\n##### 《黑暗之夜：死亡金屬》「狂笑蝙蝠 蘇打罐包裝」高4.25吋，以塑膠材料製作，並用蘇打汽水罐包裝，有六分之一的機率將可以得到夜光版本，預購價格為13.99美元。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/IStdIaw.png)\n\n\n##### 從Funko，一個PREVIEWS獨家版！笑著的蝙蝠俠是永遠勝利的蝙蝠俠！笑起來的Funko蘇打蝙蝠俠為您的DC系列增添令人耳目一新的感覺！它看起來像一罐蘇打汽水，但在罐子裡，粉絲會發現限量版4 .25吋高的塑膠模型，該模型是腐敗毒素的蝙蝠俠從黑暗多重宇宙中大笑而來，並且是可收藏的模型，另外，請注意尋找六分之一中在黑暗中追逐的有限變種版本！該PREVIEWS 獨家版人物的數量僅限於10,000件，所以請不要錯過！可能會發生分配。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/nkksLVv.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高4.25吋\n##### 預購價格：13.99美元 約396新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年6月30日\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/pziBlJY.jpg)\n\n##### From Funko. A PREVIEWS Exclusive! A Batman who laughs... is a Batman who always wins! Add a refreshing twist to your DC collection with the Funko SODA Batman Who Laughs! It looks like a can of soda pop, but inside the can, fans will find a limited edition 4 1/4-inch tall vinyl figure of the toxin-corrupted Batman Who Laughs from the Dark Multiverse and a collectible disc. Plus, look out for the one in six limited variant glow-in-the-dark chase version to hunt for and collect! Quantities of this PREVIEWS Exclusive Figure are limited to 10,000 pieces, so don\'t miss out! Allocations may occur.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/WpALZ1x.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**previewsworld**](https://www.previewsworld.com/Catalog/AUG208757)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/JwDotlr.png','https://i.imgur.com/l6jnl3V.png','新聞','2021-04-16 06:55:03',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',28,7),(577,'第二季《曼達洛人》「亞蘇卡·譚諾」普通/豪華版 1/6比例可動人偶 Hot Toys新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 世界知名的收藏級1/6比例可動人偶的香港廠牌**Hot Toys**，今日在[**粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/hottoys/)發布開放預購的 **第二季《曼達洛人》「亞蘇卡·譚諾」普通/豪華版 1/6比例可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，將於發售。\n\n\n##### 第二季《曼達洛人》「亞蘇卡·譚諾」高約29公分，配件附上光劍、2個替換頭雕、替換手、展示底座等，豪華版多附上孩子／格羅古、森林主題背景、燈籠，普通版預購價格為1,730港幣，豪華版預購價格為1,930港幣。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/gDoIQ0P.jpg)\n##### ′′格羅古和我能感受到彼此的想法。\"\n##### 在廣受歡迎的《曼達洛人》中，我們的英雄丁·賈林被追求讓神秘的寶貝格羅古回到他的同類，在他跨越銀河系的旅程中，他被引導尋找前絕地武士亞蘇卡·譚諾在科爾沃斯森林星球上《星際大戰》的粉絲們很高興看到托古塔人英雄在真人中描繪出來，第一次!\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6BaXEER.jpg)\n\n##### 為了進一步擴展《曼達洛人》收藏系列，Hot Toys很高興介紹我們驕傲的DX系列的1/6比例新收藏品，為所有《星際大戰》粉絲們提供了亞蘇卡·譚諾和格羅古!\n##### 高精度的亞蘇卡可收藏人物特色是精心製作的頭雕，具有單獨的滾眼球特徵和articulated頭尾，專業體質，量身定做的裝備，一對光劍，可替換光劍模擬武器，以及一件披風.\n##### 格羅古收藏人物有著一個新的頭雕，非常的相似，頭部和手臂具有關節。\n##### 這套特殊的特色是森林主題背景和展示底座以及燈籠，以重塑亞蘇卡和格羅古第一次見面時的難忘場景。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/LksDkKN.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：未公布，可能約29公分\n##### 預購價格：普通版1,730港幣 約6,306新台幣 豪華版1,930港幣 約7,035新台幣\n##### 發售日期：未公布\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/D8xELba.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/CAe2UfT.jpg)\n\n##### “Grogu and I can feel each other\'s thoughts.”\n##### In the widely acclaimed The Mandalorian, our hero Din Djarin™ was quested to return the mysterious baby Grogu to his kind. In his journey across the galaxy, he was guided to seek out the former Jedi™ Ahsoka Tano on the forest planet of Corvus™ where Star Wars fans were elated to see the Togruta™ hero depicted in live-action for the first time!\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VpsiQZo.jpg)\n##### To further expand The Mandalorian collectible series, Hot Toys is delighted to introduce a new 1/6th scale collectible set from our proud DX Series, featuring Ahsoka Tano and Grogu for all Star Wars fans to enjoy!\n##### The highly-accurate Ahsoka collectible figure features a meticulously crafted head sculpt with separate rolling eyeballs features and articulated head-tails, specialized physique, skillfully tailored outfit with fine details, a pair of lightsabers, interchangeable lightsaber blades emulating the weapon in motion, and a cloak.\n##### The Grogu collectible figure is featuring a newly developed head sculpt with great likeness, articulated head and arms. \n##### This special set specially features a forest theme backdrop and display base along with a lantern to recreate the memorable scene when Ahsoka and Grogu first meet.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/nbfBDvZ.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7TLaB8b.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ZXmqU0e.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/N1innsO.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/OZhyHdI.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/q6c8izm.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/gaDygy7.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/QNMOwdD.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/rigYF0v.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ToU4PNG.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/fVmDRdQ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7K3IEXG.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/WLoXpUc.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/JwVnQHn.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/w9z6ynM.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/DfD5LbJ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/va5jJoV.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VVFvDP1.jpg)\n##### 圖片來源：[**Hot Toys**](http://www.hottoys.com.hk/?fbclid=IwAR209xNQykEV9PgpXUxNqA0hV3lVOZmWez-jsVz-NYzzrhb9TQX22Rj7dlI)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/NtFXgTo.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/LwNSa1p.jpg','新聞','2021-04-16 07:46:21',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',38,7),(578,'《無敵少俠》系列1「無敵小子」、「全能人（omni man）」7吋可動人偶 Diamond Select Toys新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 美國品牌**Diamond Select Toys**主打低價位就能買到6吋左右，非常具有收藏性的雕像及可動人偶，4月10日在[**粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/diamondselecttoys/?ref=page_internal)進行2021年即將推出的產品的線上玩具展覽，其中包含 **《無敵少俠》系列1「無敵小子」、「全能人（omni man）」7吋可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，將於2021年6月發售。\n\n##### 《無敵少俠》是長期製作的漫畫系列，近期已被製作成動畫，無敵小子的父親「全能人」是長久以來的反派，無敵小子在發現自己也有超能力後決定成為超級英雄與父親對抗。\n\n##### Diamond Select Toys 2021的線上玩具展\n\n<iframe src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=314&href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdiamondselecttoys%2Fvideos%2F267154121738946%2F&show_text=true&width=560\" width=\"400\" height=\"429\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowFullScreen=\"true\"></iframe>\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/cZvgbSv.jpg)\n\n##### 尺寸：高6吋｜寬11吋｜長10吋\n##### 預購價格：單款24.99美元 約708新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年6月\n\n##### **無敵小子系列1**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/0MAgjOF.png)\n##### Diamond Select Toys發布！來自Skybound的長期漫畫系列現在是動畫系列，DST將提供全新的動作人物！嶄露頭角的超級英雄無敵小子和他的外星父親全能人組成了首批7吋的人物，每個人物都有16個關節和可替換的頭部和雙手，以及各種配件：一個混凝土塊和一個亞麻色的手臂是給全能人，一個Reanimen頭是給無敵小子，兩人都有棒球手套！每個都包裝在帶有吊牌的透明彩盒，由克里斯·達爾伯格（Chris Dahlberg）製作！\n![](https://i.imgur.com/0Lw9myq.png)\n##### A Diamond Select Toys release! The long-running comic series from Skybound is now an animated series, and DST is delivering all-new action figures! Up-and-coming superhero Invincible and his alien father Omni-Man make up the first assortment of 7-inch figures, each with 16 points of articulation and interchangeable heads and hands, as well as various accessories: a concrete block and Flaxan arm for Omni-Man, a Reanimen head for Invincible, and baseball gloves for both! Each comes packaged in a full-color window box with hangtag. Sculpted by Chris Dahlberg!\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4Nsi7UH.png)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/xo3g1Sk.png)\n\n##### **全能人（omni man）系列1**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SSPiAsZ.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/rhgftUK.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7XyjkTX.png)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Fn4yDPN.png)\n\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Diamond Select Toys**](https://www.diamondselecttoys.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/H7N8xXw.png','https://i.imgur.com/0s6sYk5.jpg','新聞','2021-04-16 09:45:18',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',205,7),(579,'《魔戒 聖盔谷之戰》「勒苟拉斯」普通/獨家版 1/6比例可動人偶 Asmus Toys新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 台灣玩具公司**Asmus Toys**，昨日發布開放預購的 **《魔戒 聖盔谷之戰》「勒苟拉斯」普通/獨家版 1/6比例可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，可以在[**官網**](http://store.asmustoys.com//)及[**Sideshow Collectibles**](https://www.sideshow.com/collectibles/the-lord-of-the-rings-legolas-at-helms-deep-asmus-collectible-toy-908182?var=9081821)進行預購，將於2021年第三季發售。\n\n##### 《魔戒 聖盔谷之戰》「勒苟拉斯」1/6比例可動人偶高30公分，全身超過34個關節點，配件附上羅漢劍、一把利古拉斯的精靈刀、一把刀鞘、一把匕首的裝飾刀柄、加拉達姆之弓、洛瑞恩的箭x 6、洛瑞顫抖、支撐架，獨家版多附上赫爾姆之深的一盞燈、強獸人戰鬥階梯的一部分、互動式立體模型，具有城堡的牆壁和樓梯，普通版預購價格為195美元，獨家版預購價格為289美元。\n\n\n##### 配件：\n##### ·一個Asmus Toys人物架\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/J8KD6jv.jpg)\n\n##### 頭盔深度深處的Legolas第六比例公仔具有 來自  兩座塔樓的Legolas 真實而詳細的完全逼真的肖像  ·約30厘米高·超過34個鉸接點特點： · Asmus Toys ADAM身體·長片中演員的真實肖像。·一對放鬆姿勢的手·一對武器握住的手·一對拳頭姿勢的手·一隻弓箭手唱歌。一隻弓箭手為雙箭頭·一對兩個零件套，增強了踝關節的清晰度\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/dGQod35.jpg)\n\n\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qo5M3e4.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高30公分\n##### 預購價格：普通版195美元 約5,526新台幣 \n##### 獨家版289美元 約8,190新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年第三季\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/RMFLAhX.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Lwc1iQA.jpg)\n\n##### The Legolas at Helm’s Deep Exclusive Edition Sixth Scale Figure features authentic and detailed fully realistic likeness of  Legolas  from  The Two Towers\n##### · Approximately 30 cm tall\n##### · Over 34 points of articulation\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/qoy7hYI.jpg)\nFeatures:\n##### · Asmus Toys ADAM body\n##### · An authentic likeness of the actor from the feature films.\n##### · One pair of relaxed posture hand\n##### · One pair of weapon holding hand\n##### · One pair of fist posture hand\n##### · One bow drawing hand for sing arrow\n##### . One bow drawing hand for double arrows\n##### · One pair of two parts boot, enhanced ankle articulation\n\n##### Special features on Clothing:\n##### · One pair of long sleeved undervest\n##### · One pair of long underpants\n##### · One green elven vest\n##### · One elven cape\n##### · One belt with scabbard\n##### . One elven belt\n##### . One pair of elven brace\n##### . One pair of Rohan shoulder armour \n\n\n##### Special features in weapons:\n\n##### . One Rohan sword\n##### · One pair of Legolas\' elvish knives\n##### · One pair of the knife sheath\n##### · One pair of dagger decorative handle of the knife\n##### · Bow of the Galadhrim\n##### · The arrows of Lórien x 6\n##### · The Lórien quiver\n\n\n##### Accessories:\n##### · One Asmus Toys figure stand\n\n##### Exclusive Edition includes:\n##### · A lamp of Helm\'s Deep\n##### . A part of Uruk-hai battle ladder\n##### · Interactive diorama featuring wall and staircase of the keep\n\n\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/B9nJ8hX.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/tTYnLYH.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7neTWjg.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Nfa6GVQ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mFFnzc0.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hHz1SlJ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/o1wPxA7.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/FmFrLIv.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/KZif7ZB.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/GiIHDzI.jpg)\n##### 圖片來源：[**Asmus Toys**](http://store.asmustoys.com//)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/f47lNCn.jpg','','新聞','2021-04-16 11:05:30',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',134,7),(580,'《忍者龜》「ACE DUCK＆突變異人（Mutagen Man）雙人包」7吋可動人偶 NECA新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### NECA(國家娛樂收藏品協會)，4月16日發布開放預購的 **《忍者龜》「ACE DUCK＆突變異人（Mutagen Man）雙人包」7吋可動人偶**官方圖片與訊息，預購時間到4月25日，現在可以在[**The NECA Store**](https://thenecastore.com/)進行預購，將於2021年秋季發售。\n\n《忍者龜》「ACE DUCK＆突變異人（Mutagen Man）雙人包」高7吋，突變異人配件附上可替換的表情，坦克和武器配件，ACE DUCK配件附上兩個手槍、飛行員帽、VHS膠帶、膠片捲軸、替換頭雕。\n\n##### 基於經典的1980年代《忍者龜》卡通系列！在意外暴露於放射性軟泥之後，四隻普通的家庭寵物變成了一群狡猾的，喜歡披薩，反派切丁的青少年爬行動物！無論是面對兇猛的敵人還是要拯救人類免於滅絕，在他們的師傅的指導下，這些“半殼英雄”終於可以直接衝出下水道！\n##### 笨拙的送貨員西摩·古茨（Seymour Gutz）偶然偶然發現了切瑞德的秘密實驗室，掉進了軟泥裡，變成了突變的男人，他會重獲人形嗎，會成為海龜的朋友或敵人嗎？突變異人帶有可替換的表情，坦克和武器配件。 \n##### 當海龜需要從所有動作中休息時，他們將參加由空氣動力冒險家Ace Duck主演的電影節 ！\n##### Ace帶有機翼，兩個手槍、飛行員帽、VHS膠帶、膠片捲軸、替換頭雕。\n\n\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/pmPCS89.jpg)\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高7吋\n##### 預購價格：51.99美元 約1,465新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年秋季\n\n##### Based on the classic 1980s Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles cartoon series! After being accidentally exposed to radioactive ooze, four ordinary household pets are transformed into a band of wisecracking, pizza-loving, villain-dicing adolescent reptiles! Whether it\'s facing fierce enemies or saving humanity from near extinction, with the guidance of their Sensei, these Heroes in a Half Shell are always ready for straight outta the sewer action!\n##### Clumsy delivery man Seymour Gutz accidentally stumbles upon Shredder\'s secret lab and falls into a tank of ooze, becoming Mutagen Man. Will he ever regain his human form, and will he be friend or foe to the Turtles? Mutagen Man comes with swappable face, tank and weapon accessories. \n##### When the Turtles need a break from all the action, they check out a film festival starring Ace Duck, the aerodynamic adventurer!\n##### Ace comes with wings, two service pistols, pilot\'s cap, VHS tape, film reel, and alternate head.\n\n\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**The NECA Store**](https://thenecastore.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/mkbl7GP.png','https://i.imgur.com/3r10pEH.png','新聞','2021-04-19 03:56:51',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',34,7),(581,'《蜘蛛人：驚奇再起》「蜘蛛人衝擊系列A版＆B版」1/7比例收藏雕像 XM Studios＆Legendary Beast Studios新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 新加坡雕像廠牌**XM Studios**與菲律賓廠牌Legendary Beast Studios合作，昨日發布 **《變形金剛》《蜘蛛人：驚奇再起》「蜘蛛人衝擊系列A版＆B版」1/7比例收藏雕像**官方圖片與訊息，現在可以在[**XM Studios**](https://www.xm-studios.com/pages/default.aspx)與[**Legendary Beast Studios**](http://legendarybeaststudios.com/)進行預購，將於2022年第二季發售。\n\n##### 《蜘蛛人：驚奇再起》「蜘蛛人衝擊系列A版＆B版」1/7比例收藏雕像高38公分，A版與B版差在爆炸效果的呈現方式，A版是不透明的特效，B版是半透明的特效，並具有LED照明功能，A版預購價格為34,500菲律賓比索，B版預購價格為36,500菲律賓比索，各限量400件。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/P6LNbPF.jpg)\n\n##### 為了避開某些危險，我們友好的鄰居蜘蛛人利用他敏捷的身體來避免兇猛的機械蜘蛛蜘蛛！這個雕像展示了詳細的爆炸效果，隨處可見蜘蛛爪零件，該雕像充分彰顯了我們英雄的蜘蛛感應，因為他輕鬆躲避了每個射彈。\n\n\n##### 彼得·帕克被放射性蜘蛛咬傷，為他提供了驚人的力量，可以用來幫助他人，而他的個人生活繼續為他製造許多障礙。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 尺寸：高38公分｜寬36公分｜長54公分\n##### 預購價格：A版34,500菲律賓比索 約20,074新台幣\n##### B版36,500菲律賓比索 約21,237新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2022年第二季\n\n##### **●蜘蛛人衝擊系列A版**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/rW3KGmF.jpg)\n##### 版本A將突出顯示許多收藏家習慣的蜘蛛機器人爆炸的樹脂塗裝特效，這將使收藏家們期望獲得高細節塗裝的收藏。\n\n##### 除了爆炸效果，這兩個版本完全相同，因此請選擇您想要的東西。甚至更好，兩者都選！！\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Xm9ERKU.jpg)\n##### –複雜而詳細的樹脂雕像，具有被毀壞的街道場景，其中有反派蜘蛛機器人和標誌性蜘蛛人，均採用環繞式網狀設計。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/X9MuWFC.jpg)\n##### Version A will highlight the RESIN ONLY paint effect for the Spider-bot explosion that many collectors are used to. This will have the high detailed paint application collectors have come to expect in their collection.\n![](https://i.imgur.com/iKfAk5C.jpg)\n##### – A Complex and detailed Polystone Statue featuring A destroyed street base scene with the Villainous Spider-Bot and Iconic Spider-man featuring his wrap around web design.\n![](https://i.imgur.com/u21rdkg.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NrxY2Rv.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/37xgX96.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/nKR19HC.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/FiZ41vN.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/u4omoWo.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ILyPLTE.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/clyVE3X.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/tCPYvON.jpg)\n\n\n\n\n##### **●蜘蛛人衝擊系列B版**\n![](https://i.imgur.com/cBECK2x.jpg)\n##### 版本B適用於那些希望在透明樹脂版本中具有更多獨占性的用戶，唯一使用這種具有照明功能的出色樹脂的版本，它可以使爆炸性細節以雕像中從未見過的方式脫穎而出，點亮功能將帶出紅色、橙色、黃色，可在白天或晚上進行詳細觀看。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VnkdXSk.jpg)\n##### –複雜而詳細的樹脂雕像，具有被毀壞的街道場景，其中有反派蜘蛛機器人和標誌性蜘蛛人，均採用環繞式網狀設計。\n##### –此版本是透明樹脂爆炸效果，具有獨家照明功能，從內部突出的爆炸。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/cnJHDEN.jpg)\n##### Version B is for those of you wanting something a bit more exclusive in the clear resin version. The only version to use this brilliant resin with a light feature that will make the explosive detail stand out in a way not seen before in statues. The light up feature will bring out the reds, oranges and yellows that can be seen in detail day or night.\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6c7Vdik.jpg)\n##### – A Complex and detailed Polystone Statue featuring A destroyed street base scene with the Villainous Spider-Bot and Iconic Spider-man featuring his wrap around web design.\n##### – This Version will be CLEAR RESIN ONLY explosion effect. Featuring Exclusive Light Up feature to highlight the explosion from within.\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mKY3Qyq.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/OhUVaC0.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SgZM4MW.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ZN23yBR.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3HXV8Hf.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/F5FVS70.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/2JXtXFS.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/BKN9xl4.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ADTwF9p.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/XkaeTss.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/iCrd7VA.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hZr7hVb.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/RTnsenf.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/0ECEHD5.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/DERBBLY.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/DoboFNx.jpg)\n\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Legendary Beast Studios**](http://legendarybeaststudios.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/djCXPag.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/cY2c9Z6.jpg','新聞','2021-04-19 04:43:06',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',28,7),(582,'犯罪王子《DC漫畫》「小丑」普通版1/10比例藝術雕像 Iron Studios新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 販售各種流行文化人物的雕像品牌**Iron Studios**，4月17日發布 **《DC漫畫》「小丑」普通版1/10比例藝術雕像**官方圖片與訊息，現在可以在[**官網**](https://ironstudios.com/)進行預購，將於2021年第三季發售。\n\n\n\n##### \n![](https://i.imgur.com/goioL9H.jpg)\n\n##### The Joker擁有更現代的外觀，但又不忘他的背景，融合了色彩和經典元素，穿著紫色，配以橙色襯衫、綠色吊帶、黑色領帶，還得到了Iron Studios的另一個版本，該版本取自DC漫畫。\n\n \n\n##### 在底座上，他擺姿勢好像他在鋼瓶、連接件、管道之間行走，這是指小人的出生地哥譚市的“王牌化工廠”的場景，巴塔朗腳下的金屬球被卡住，雕像“The Joker Art Scale 1/10 – DC Comics”向犯罪王子王子展示了他鮮明的動作微笑，右手握著一把撬棍，他在漫畫中最難忘的時刻之一使用的工具，並準備從翻領上的花朵中拍攝一些化學和酸性物質，這是他的另一個商標。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/lVkJ4c3.jpg)\n \n\n##### 小丑是漫畫界最偉大的惡棍之一，也是蝙蝠俠最偉大的敵人，小丑是由比爾·芬格，鮑勃·凱恩和傑瑞·羅賓遜創作的，其靈感來自演員康拉德·韋德特在1928年的電影《大笑的男人》和一張撲克牌中，瘋狂且始終微笑著，他於1940年在蝙蝠俠＃1中首次亮相，他的血統以及他的真實姓名至今仍是個謎。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3EHWYgE.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高9吋｜寬5.5吋｜長4.7吋\n##### 預購價格：129.99美元 約3,655新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年第三季\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/DmYEuWR.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/T7bArLB.jpg)\n##### With a more contemporary look, but without forgetting his background, combining colors and classic elements, dressed in purple, complemented with an orange shirt, green suspenders, and a black tie, The Joker gets one more version derived from DC Comics, by Iron Studios.\n\n \n\n##### On a base, he poses as if he is walking between cylinders, connections, and pipes, which refers to the scenario of “Ace Chemical Transformation Factory” in Gotham City, the villain’s birthplace. With a Batarang stuck in a metallic sphere at his feet, the statue “The Joker Art Scale 1/10 DC Comics – Iron Studios” presents the Prince Clown of Crime with his unmistakable smile in action, carrying a crowbar in his right fist, the tool used in one of his most memorable moments in the comics, and ready to shoot some chemical and acidic substance, from the flower in his lapel, another one of his trademarks.\n\n \n![](https://i.imgur.com/g4xhNBl.jpg)\n\n##### One of the greatest villains in comics, and Batman’s greatest archenemy, The Joker was created by Bill Finger, Bob Kane, and Jerry Robinson, inspired by actor Conrad Veidt in the 1928 film “The Man Who Laughs” and a playing card. Crazy and always smiling, he made his debut in Batman #1 in 1940. His origin, as well as his real name, are a mystery to this day.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/raUBV9O.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/9tLaVPx.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VNe0Y4g.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/YhTCgs4.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/uEVKjzv.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/GhKEgWR.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Ibl5Tdc.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ID2FaDp.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/MiJG9nw.jpg)\n\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Iron Studios**](https://ironstudios.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/qSZ57Gs.png','https://i.imgur.com/Z7UYTUa.png','新聞','2021-04-19 12:59:02',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',37,7),(583,'犯罪王子《DC漫畫》「小丑」豪華版1/10比例藝術雕像 Iron Studios新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 販售各種流行文化人物的雕像品牌**Iron Studios**，4月17日發布 **《DC漫畫》「小丑」豪華版1/10比例藝術雕像**官方圖片與訊息，現在可以在[**官網**](https://ironstudios.com/)進行預購，將於2021年第三季發售。\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NqlLBfQ.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### The Joker擁有更現代的外觀，但又不忘他的背景，融合了色彩和經典元素，穿著紫色，配以橙色襯衫，綠色吊帶和黑色領帶，還得到了Iron Studios的另一個版本，該版本取自DC漫畫。\n\n \n\n##### 彷彿他正行走在一個裝有鋼瓶，連接件和管道的底座上，並且有氣體通過它們的結合處逸出，這就是小人的出生地哥譚市“王牌化工廠”的場景，還有他的紫色軟呢帽帽子，放在鋼瓶上，巴塔朗腳下的金屬球被卡住，雕像“The Joker Art Scale 1/10 – DC Comics”向犯罪王子王子展示了鮮明的動作微笑，右手握著一把撬棍，這是他在漫畫中最難忘的時刻中使用的工具，並準備從翻領上的花朵中拍攝一些化學和酸性物質，這是他的另一個商標。\n\n \n![](https://i.imgur.com/8aL0Yiw.jpg)\n\n##### 小丑是漫畫界最偉大的惡棍之一，也是蝙蝠俠最偉大的敵人，小丑是由比爾·芬格，鮑勃·凱恩和傑瑞·羅賓遜創作的，其靈感來自演員康拉德·韋德特在1928年的電影《大笑的男人》和一張撲克牌中。瘋狂且始終微笑著，他於1940年在蝙蝠俠＃1中首次亮相，他的血統以及他的真實姓名至今仍是個謎。\n\n點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/F1VAcmB.jpg)\n\n\n\n##### 尺寸：高9吋｜寬5.5吋｜長4.7吋\n##### 預購價格：169.99美元 約4,784新台幣\n##### 發售日期：2021年第三季\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/nJnDc9L.jpg)\n\n##### 點擊[**首頁**](https://stubbornnews.com/frontend/index.html)看更多新聞\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6il90Zp.jpg)\n\n##### With a more contemporary look, but without forgetting his background, combining colors and classic elements, dressed in purple, complemented with an orange shirt, green suspenders, and a black tie, The Joker gets one more version derived from DC Comics, by Iron Studios.\n\n \n\n##### As if he is walking on a base with cylinders, connections, and pipes, with gases escaping through the junction of them, which refers to the scene of the “Ace Chemical Transformation Factory” in Gotham City, the villain’s birthplace, with his purple fedora hat and resting on a containment cylinder. With a Batarang stuck in a metallic sphere at his feet, the statue “The Joker Deluxe Art Scale 1/10 DC Comics – Iron Studios” presents the Prince Clown of Crime with his unmistakable smile in action, carrying a crowbar in his right fist, the tool used in one of his most memorable moments in the comics, and ready to shoot some chemical and acidic substance, from the flower in his lapel, another one of his trademarks.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/2VwLn6g.jpg)\n \n\n##### One of the greatest villains in comics, and Batman’s greatest archenemy, The Joker was created by Bill Finger, Bob Kane, and Jerry Robinson, inspired by actor Conrad Veidt in the 1928 film “The Man Who Laughs” and a playing card. Crazy and always smiling, he made his debut in Batman #1 in 1940. His origin, as well as his real name, are a mystery to this day.\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/VhO4xtX.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/b3Nnm7G.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/agvoVxu.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/t7CxBUW.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/oeuwQG5.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mWgRGKC.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wwRXovL.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/jQd4Wur.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NqtUaPW.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/kXPRyG6.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/DzoS49y.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wDHGmwl.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/v58B8tX.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1iy0GjI.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/41IgLy9.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NnTFZJ4.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/04KYSZB.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/GTGblwN.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ymtpRyG.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6qpk6TU.jpg)\n\n##### 圖片來源：[**Iron Studios**](https://ironstudios.com/)\n##### 想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)','https://i.imgur.com/0TMBPVv.png','https://i.imgur.com/XlDwimE.png','新聞','2021-04-19 12:59:43',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',51,7),(586,'第五季《冰與火之歌：權力遊戲》「丹妮莉絲·坦格利安」1/6比例可動人偶 Threezero新品','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑 Stubborn Toy News粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257